Dialogue: 3,0:00:22.52,0:00:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}只有富人才能在这个国家做生意
Dialogue: 2,0:00:22.52,0:00:24.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Only the rich can do business in this country.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:26.88,0:00:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因为这条路上有许多巨大的陷阱
Dialogue: 2,0:00:26.88,0:00:29.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Because there are huge pitfalls along this road.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:31.92,0:00:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}小贩和商人很容易就走进陷阱
Dialogue: 2,0:00:31.92,0:00:34.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}A trader or a businessman can easily fall into them.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:37.32,0:00:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在这条路上诚信和努力工作是不可能成功的
Dialogue: 2,0:00:37.32,0:00:40.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's impossible to run a business on this road with honesty and hard work.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:42.36,0:00:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是有一个办法..
Dialogue: 2,0:00:42.36,0:00:43.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But there is a way...
Dialogue: 3,0:00:44.00,0:00:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一条捷径
Dialogue: 2,0:00:44.00,0:00:45.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...a shortcut.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:46.12,0:00:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这条捷径直通德里的议会大厦
Dialogue: 2,0:00:46.12,0:00:47.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Which goes via Delhi's parliament house.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:49.28,0:00:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}有了关系，你可以做任何事情
Dialogue: 2,0:00:49.28,0:00:50.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}With connections, you can get anything done.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:52.48,0:00:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}重要的是，谁是你的关系网..
Dialogue: 2,0:00:52.48,0:00:55.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What's important is, who are your connections...
Dialogue: 3,0:00:55.68,0:00:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们的地位有多高
Dialogue: 2,0:00:55.68,0:00:56.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...and how high up they are.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:58.20,0:01:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们的影响力越大..
Dialogue: 2,0:00:58.20,0:01:00.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The more influential they are...
Dialogue: 3,0:01:00.36,0:01:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你的生意就会越做越好
Dialogue: 2,0:01:00.36,0:01:02.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...the higher your business will soar.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:05.64,0:01:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我也有一张德里的权力关系网
Dialogue: 2,0:01:05.64,0:01:08.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I have also paid my respects in the power portals of Delhi.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:10.88,0:01:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我和德里的关系是悠久而深厚的
Dialogue: 2,0:01:10.88,0:01:13.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}My relationship with Delhi is old and very deep.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:15.92,0:01:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在91届选举期间..
Dialogue: 2,0:01:15.92,0:01:17.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}During the 91 elections...
Dialogue: 3,0:01:18.28,0:01:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们给这个政党捐了很多钱
Dialogue: 2,0:01:18.28,0:01:20.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...we gave a lot of donation to the party.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:21.12,0:01:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一大笔钱
Dialogue: 2,0:01:21.12,0:01:22.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Large sums.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:23.96,0:01:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}从政党顾问到首相，每个人都知道
Dialogue: 2,0:01:23.96,0:01:27.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And everyone is aware of this, from the party's advisor to the Prime Minister.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:29.52,0:01:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以当补选日期宣布后
Dialogue: 2,0:01:29.52,0:01:31.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And so when the by-election dates were declared...
Dialogue: 3,0:01:32.32,0:01:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我和萨哈布谈过
Dialogue: 2,0:01:32.32,0:01:33.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...I spoke to Sahab.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:35.64,0:01:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我去向他致敬
Dialogue: 2,0:01:35.64,0:01:37.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And I went to pay my respects to him.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:40.60,0:01:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}英德拉吉·夏尔马
Dialogue: 2,0:01:40.60,0:01:41.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Indrajit Sharma.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:43.68,0:01:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}首相联合秘书
Dialogue: 2,0:01:43.68,0:01:45.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Joint secretary to PM.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:46.76,0:01:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他是安排会议的人
Dialogue: 2,0:01:46.76,0:01:48.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He was the one who fixed the meeting.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:50.48,0:01:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那天是1991年11月4日
Dialogue: 2,0:01:50.48,0:01:52.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The date was 4th November, 1991.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:14.88,0:02:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“我在想，首相为什么要见我? ”
Dialogue: 2,0:02:14.88,0:02:16.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad]'I was wondering why would the Prime Minister meet me?'
Dialogue: 3,0:02:16.88,0:02:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“他会跟我谈什么? ”
Dialogue: 2,0:02:16.88,0:02:17.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'What will he talk to me about?'
Dialogue: 3,0:02:19.24,0:02:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但他知道我的一切
Dialogue: 2,0:02:19.24,0:02:20.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But he knew everything about me.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:22.84,0:02:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他一见到我就说..
Dialogue: 2,0:02:22.84,0:02:24.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}As soon as he met me, he said...
Dialogue: 3,0:02:25.12,0:02:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“哈沙德，我党视你们为朋友”
Dialogue: 2,0:02:25.12,0:02:30.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}..."Harshad, our party has seen you people like our friends."
Dialogue: 3,0:02:31.32,0:02:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“我们可以一起做一番大事”
Dialogue: 2,0:02:31.32,0:02:33.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"And together we can do bigger things."
Dialogue: 3,0:02:34.28,0:02:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但现在，警察和中央调查局
Dialogue: 2,0:02:34.28,0:02:36.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But today, the police, CBI...
Dialogue: 3,0:02:36.84,0:02:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还有政府的其他部门，都只追捕一个人
Dialogue: 2,0:02:36.84,0:02:39.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...and every other agency of the government is only after one man.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:41.00,0:02:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈尔沙德 · 梅塔
Dialogue: 2,0:02:41.00,0:02:41.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad Mehta.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:44.32,0:02:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}为什么? 因为我诈骗？
Dialogue: 2,0:02:44.32,0:02:46.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Why? Because I've done a scam?
Dialogue: 3,0:02:47.00,0:02:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不，原因是..
Dialogue: 2,0:02:47.00,0:02:48.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No. The reason is that...
Dialogue: 3,0:02:49.20,0:02:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我很了解这个国家的总理
Dialogue: 2,0:02:49.20,0:02:50.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...I know a lot about the country's Prime Minister...
Dialogue: 3,0:02:51.28,0:02:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还有这个党派的其他人
Dialogue: 2,0:02:51.28,0:02:53.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...and about many others in this party.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:53.88,0:02:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我知道真相
Dialogue: 2,0:02:53.88,0:02:54.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And I know the truth.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:58.64,0:03:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}由于巴布里清真寺被拆毁，暴乱仍在继续..
Dialogue: 2,0:02:58.64,0:03:01.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Riots are going on because of the Babri Masjid demolition...
Dialogue: 3,0:03:02.12,0:03:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但我的家人更怕 CBI 而不是暴乱
Dialogue: 2,0:03:02.12,0:03:04.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...but my family is more scared of the CBI than the riots.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:08.16,0:03:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}中央调查局可以对我和我的家人做任何事
Dialogue: 2,0:03:08.16,0:03:10.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}CBI can do anything to me and my family.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:13.68,0:03:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我拍这个视频是因为，如果我出了什么事..
Dialogue: 2,0:03:13.68,0:03:17.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I am shooting this video so that, if something happens to me...
Dialogue: 3,0:03:17.44,0:03:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}人们应该知道幕后黑手是谁
Dialogue: 2,0:03:17.44,0:03:19.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...people should know who is behind it.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:23.64,0:04:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你在干什么，米什拉？
Dialogue: 2,0:04:23.64,0:04:24.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What are you doing, Mishra?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:26.52,0:04:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}怎么把他打成这样？
Dialogue: 2,0:04:26.52,0:04:27.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}How much did you hit him?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:28.24,0:04:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你没长脑子吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:04:28.24,0:04:29.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Is your brain between your legs?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:32.16,0:04:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}看看他的脸，像钟上的6:05一样倾斜
Dialogue: 2,0:04:32.16,0:04:34.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Madhavan] 'Look at his face. It's tilted like 6:05 on a clock.'
Dialogue: 3,0:04:35.56,0:04:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}布尚不是一个呆子
Dialogue: 2,0:04:35.56,0:04:36.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Bhushan ji is not a goon.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:37.12,0:04:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果他说得清楚，我就让他走，但是他不愿意开口
Dialogue: 2,0:04:37.12,0:04:39.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If he spoke clearly, I'd let him go. But he's not willing to talk.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:40.04,0:04:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我该说什么? 我应该说什么语言？
Dialogue: 2,0:04:40.04,0:04:43.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What do I say? In what language should I speak?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:44.16,0:04:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你们这些人到底懂不懂？
Dialogue: 2,0:04:44.16,0:04:46.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Do you people even understand anything?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:46.84,0:04:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}布尚先生，你不是呆子
Dialogue: 2,0:04:46.84,0:04:48.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Bhushan ji, you're not a goon.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:49.96,0:04:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你是个混蛋
Dialogue: 2,0:04:49.96,0:04:52.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You're a p**p.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:54.76,0:04:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你和你的老板把市场搞得一团糟
Dialogue: 2,0:04:54.76,0:04:57.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You and your boss have turned the market into a br***el.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:58.60,0:04:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“对吧? ”
Dialogue: 2,0:04:58.60,0:04:59.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Madhavan] 'Right?'
Dialogue: 3,0:05:00.16,0:05:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}谁能理解混蛋说了什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:05:00.16,0:05:01.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And who understands what a p**p says?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:02.40,0:05:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}只有妓女
Dialogue: 2,0:05:02.40,0:05:04.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Only the prostitutes.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:04.92,0:05:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}看看他们，他们像妓女吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:05:04.92,0:05:07.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look at them. Do they look like prostitutes?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:08.72,0:05:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}用他们能听懂的语言交谈
Dialogue: 2,0:05:08.72,0:05:10.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Talk in a language that they'll understand.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:12.00,0:05:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 这是商业语言...-闭嘴！
Dialogue: 2,0:05:12.00,0:05:13.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- This is the language of the business... - Shut up!
Dialogue: 3,0:05:14.12,0:05:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}生意... 生意... 生意！
Dialogue: 2,0:05:14.12,0:05:15.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Business... business... business!
Dialogue: 3,0:05:16.20,0:05:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你当我们是白痴吗！
Dialogue: 2,0:05:16.20,0:05:17.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Do you think we are a******s!
Dialogue: 3,0:05:18.00,0:05:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们知道你是做什么生意的
Dialogue: 2,0:05:18.00,0:05:19.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We know what business you do.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:23.08,0:05:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}看看他们，看看他们的脸
Dialogue: 2,0:05:23.08,0:05:25.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look at them. Look at their faces.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:25.60,0:05:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们只有一个目标，那就是击败哈尔沙德 · 梅塔
Dialogue: 2,0:05:25.60,0:05:28.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They have just one goal and that is to sc**w Harshad Mehta.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:29.48,0:05:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但那是不可能的，所以在那之前..
Dialogue: 2,0:05:29.48,0:05:31.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But that is not happening, so till then...
Dialogue: 3,0:05:31.92,0:05:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们会搞死你的，明白吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:05:31.92,0:05:33.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...we'll sc**w you. Got it?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:35.24,0:05:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果你明白了... 开始说吧
Dialogue: 2,0:05:35.24,0:05:36.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If you've understood... Start talking.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:37.36,0:05:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}’说’ ，’说’ . . 我该说什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:05:37.36,0:05:39.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Talk', 'Talk'..? What should I say?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:39.68,0:05:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“小声点! ”
Dialogue: 2,0:05:39.68,0:05:40.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[CBI Officer] 'Lower your voice!'
Dialogue: 3,0:05:42.88,0:05:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你看起来很生气
Dialogue: 2,0:05:42.88,0:05:44.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You seem angry.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:45.08,0:05:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}别生气，布尚先生，这是我们的工作
Dialogue: 2,0:05:45.08,0:05:47.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Don't get mad, Bhushan ji. That's our job.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:49.28,0:05:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}去拿条毛巾，拿条毛巾
Dialogue: 2,0:05:49.28,0:05:51.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Go and get a towel. Get a towel.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:51.56,0:05:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}看他流了多少汗，你快把他打成肉酱了！
Dialogue: 2,0:05:51.56,0:05:53.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look how much he's sweating. You have beaten him to a pulp!
Dialogue: 3,0:05:55.16,0:05:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“别生气”
Dialogue: 2,0:05:55.16,0:05:56.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Madhavan] 'Don't get angry.'
Dialogue: 3,0:05:57.00,0:05:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}去拿毛巾
Dialogue: 2,0:05:57.00,0:05:57.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Get the towel.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:59.04,0:05:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}擦擦脸
Dialogue: 2,0:05:59.04,0:05:59.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Wipe your face.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:01.84,0:06:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}继续，擦擦你的脸
Dialogue: 2,0:06:01.84,0:06:03.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Madhavan] 'Go on, wipe your face.'
Dialogue: 3,0:06:05.56,0:06:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:06:05.56,0:06:07.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What is this?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:07.84,0:06:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}怎么了? 你在上面撒尿了？
Dialogue: 2,0:06:07.84,0:06:09.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Madhavan laughs] What happened? Did you piss on it?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:10.28,0:06:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你们是中央调查局的员工还是一群狗？
Dialogue: 2,0:06:10.28,0:06:13.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Are you the CBI, or a pack of dogs?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:13.44,0:06:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你想在哪儿撒尿就在哪儿撒
Dialogue: 2,0:06:13.44,0:06:15.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You piss wherever you like.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:15.72,0:06:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我让你用水把毛巾弄湿，不是用尿
Dialogue: 2,0:06:15.72,0:06:17.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I asked you to wet the towel with water, not with piss.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:18.24,0:06:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你甚至不知道怎么审问
Dialogue: 2,0:06:18.24,0:06:20.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You don't even know how to interrogate.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:21.88,0:06:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}至少，提出正确的问题
Dialogue: 2,0:06:21.88,0:06:24.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}At least, ask the right questions.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:25.48,0:06:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们问错问题了，是吗? 好吧
Dialogue: 2,0:06:25.48,0:06:28.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We are asking the wrong questions, is it? Okay.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:29.24,0:06:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们会问正确的问题
Dialogue: 2,0:06:29.24,0:06:30.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We'll ask the right question.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:30.44,0:06:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}米什拉，什么是正确的问题？
Dialogue: 2,0:06:30.44,0:06:32.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Mishra ji, what's the right question these days?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:34.48,0:06:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}伊路，伊路... ..
Dialogue: 2,0:06:34.48,0:06:35.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Mishra] 'Ilu, Ilu...'
Dialogue: 3,0:06:35.80,0:06:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}伊路，伊路
Dialogue: 2,0:06:35.80,0:06:36.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Ilu, Ilu.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:37.24,0:06:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}伊路是什么，伊路? 对，我应该问你吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:06:37.24,0:06:40.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What is Ilu, Ilu? Right. Should I ask you that?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:40.96,0:06:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}伊路到底是什么? 我该问你这个问题吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:06:40.96,0:06:44.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What the f**k is Ilu Ilu? Should I ask you that question?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:44.32,0:06:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你能回答吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:06:44.32,0:06:45.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Will you answer that?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:46.72,0:06:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}该死的混蛋
Dialogue: 2,0:06:46.72,0:06:47.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}F*****g p**p.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:48.12,0:06:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在我只是用尿擦了你的脸
Dialogue: 2,0:06:48.12,0:06:49.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}For now I've only wiped your face with piss.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:50.04,0:06:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果你耍小聪明，我就直接在你脸上撒尿
Dialogue: 2,0:06:50.04,0:06:52.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If you act smart, I'll piss on your face.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:56.48,0:06:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果哈沙德知道了，他会让你们所有人付出代价的
Dialogue: 2,0:06:56.48,0:06:58.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}When Harshad finds out, he'll make everyone pay for it.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:01.76,0:07:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}让我离开这里
Dialogue: 2,0:07:01.76,0:07:03.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Let me get out of here.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:06.36,0:07:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}德里在他的掌控之中
Dialogue: 2,0:07:06.36,0:07:08.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Delhi is in his pocket.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:08.68,0:07:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的，哈沙德是老板，对吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:07:08.68,0:07:09.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yes, Harshad is the boss, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:10.44,0:07:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}德里是他的囊中之物
Dialogue: 2,0:07:10.44,0:07:11.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He has Delhi in his pocket.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:12.52,0:07:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我会把他从德里带来的所有人都关进监狱，明白吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:07:12.52,0:07:14.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'll put all his p***ps from Delhi behind bars too, got it?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:18.64,0:07:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你能让首相..
Dialogue: 2,0:07:18.64,0:07:20.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Would you put the Prime Minister...
Dialogue: 3,0:07:21.28,0:07:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}... 也被关进监狱？
Dialogue: 2,0:07:21.28,0:07:22.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...behind bars too?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:28.76,0:07:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}出去走走
Dialogue: 2,0:07:28.76,0:07:29.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Step outside.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:40.32,0:07:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你说什么? 首相怎么了？
Dialogue: 2,0:07:40.32,0:07:42.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What did you say? What about the Prime Minister?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:43.72,0:07:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你疯了吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:07:43.72,0:07:45.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Are you out of your mind, Madhavan?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:45.68,0:07:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你知道你在说什么吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:07:45.68,0:07:47.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Do you have any idea what you're saying?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:47.44,0:07:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，为什么你看起来很惊讶？
Dialogue: 2,0:07:47.44,0:07:49.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, why do you look surprised?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:50.32,0:07:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们又不是在月球上找到水
Dialogue: 2,0:07:50.32,0:07:52.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's not like we've found water on the moon, sir.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:52.44,0:07:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这个我们一直都知道
Dialogue: 2,0:07:52.44,0:07:53.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This, we have known all along...
Dialogue: 3,0:07:54.16,0:07:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈沙德可能有很大的政治关系，仅此而已
Dialogue: 2,0:07:54.16,0:07:56.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...that Harshad might have big political connections. That's it.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:57.24,0:08:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈沙德的一个手下告诉你，首相支持他
Dialogue: 2,0:07:57.24,0:08:00.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}One of Harshad's men tells you that the PM backs him.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:00.48,0:08:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那么，你现在要去突袭首相府？
Dialogue: 2,0:08:00.48,0:08:03.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, you're going to raid 7 RCR now? Huh?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:04.88,0:08:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你为什么对首相这么着迷？
Dialogue: 2,0:08:04.88,0:08:06.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What's this obsession that you have with Prime Ministers?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:07.04,0:08:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，根据我以前的经验，我知道..
Dialogue: 2,0:08:07.04,0:08:10.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, from my previous experiences, I know...
Dialogue: 3,0:08:10.56,0:08:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不可能突袭首相府
Dialogue: 2,0:08:10.56,0:08:13.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...that it's not possible to raid 7, Race Course Road.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:13.88,0:08:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是，先生，我们至少可以开始初步调查
Dialogue: 2,0:08:13.88,0:08:16.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But sir, we can start a primary enquiry. At least that.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:17.04,0:08:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}-马德文，你不是认真的吧-我是认真的先生
Dialogue: 2,0:08:17.04,0:08:20.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Madhavan, y-you're not serious. - I'm serious, sir.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:21.48,0:08:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我的幽默感完全与政治无关，这个案子正在转向政治
Dialogue: 2,0:08:21.48,0:08:25.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And my sense of humour is completely apolitical and this case is turning political.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:25.84,0:08:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}听我说完，先生
Dialogue: 2,0:08:25.84,0:08:26.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Madhavan] 'Just hear me out, sir.'
Dialogue: 3,0:08:27.20,0:08:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我百分之百确定，布尚是可以开口的
Dialogue: 2,0:08:27.20,0:08:30.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm 100 percent sure, Bhushan Bhatt can be our approver.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:30.96,0:08:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果我们多招待他几天，他就会开始讲所有的细节了
Dialogue: 2,0:08:30.96,0:08:33.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If we host him a bit more, he'll start singing all the details.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:34.48,0:08:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“就是这样”
Dialogue: 2,0:08:34.48,0:08:35.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Madhavan] 'It's done.'
Dialogue: 3,0:08:37.20,0:08:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你得悠着点，马德文
Dialogue: 2,0:08:37.20,0:08:38.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You need to slow down, Madhavan.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:41.32,0:08:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ Das ]“让我想一想”
Dialogue: 2,0:08:41.32,0:08:42.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Das] 'Let me think it through.'
Dialogue: 3,0:08:44.72,0:08:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}悠着点，长官? 我们就快成功了
Dialogue: 2,0:08:44.72,0:08:48.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Slow down, sir? We are almost there.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:51.60,0:08:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是托管人要求的资产清单
Dialogue: 2,0:08:51.60,0:08:55.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This is the list of assets that the custodian has asked for.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:55.80,0:08:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我让狱卒交给你签字
Dialogue: 2,0:08:55.80,0:08:58.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'll give it to the jailer. Sign them.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:01.04,0:09:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}房产、汽车、股票..
Dialogue: 2,0:09:01.04,0:09:02.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Properties, cars, shares...
Dialogue: 3,0:09:03.56,0:09:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}兄弟，他们已经把所有东西都查出来了
Dialogue: 2,0:09:03.56,0:09:06.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Bhai, they've have attached everything.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:10.64,0:09:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们把雷克萨斯也写上了吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:09:10.64,0:09:11.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Have they attached the Lexus too?
Dialogue: 3,0:09:12.44,0:09:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}别想了
Dialogue: 2,0:09:12.44,0:09:13.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Don't think about it.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:14.92,0:09:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一旦你出来了，我们再挨个收拾他们
Dialogue: 2,0:09:14.92,0:09:16.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Once you are out, we'll deal with everyone.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:17.28,0:09:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}别担心
Dialogue: 2,0:09:17.28,0:09:18.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:20.24,0:09:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}有中央的消息吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:09:20.24,0:09:21.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Any news from Swami ji?
Dialogue: 3,0:09:22.72,0:09:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们已经给了他很多钱
Dialogue: 2,0:09:22.72,0:09:23.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We have given him a lot of money.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:24.08,0:09:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}吃的人得到庄稼，收获的人得到上帝
Dialogue: 2,0:09:24.08,0:09:27.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He who eats, gets the crop. He who reaps, gets God.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:29.44,0:09:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不管我什么时候给他打电话，他的门徒都说他在冥想
Dialogue: 2,0:09:29.44,0:09:32.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Whenever I call Swami ji, his disciples say he is meditating.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:32.88,0:09:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}说他会回电话的
Dialogue: 2,0:09:32.88,0:09:33.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That he will call back.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:34.96,0:09:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不知道他要冥想多久
Dialogue: 2,0:09:34.96,0:09:36.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I don't know how long he is going to meditate.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:41.88,0:09:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在，不要给任何人一分钱
Dialogue: 2,0:09:41.88,0:09:43.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Now, not another penny to anyone.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:45.80,0:09:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}适可而止
Dialogue: 2,0:09:45.80,0:09:46.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Enough is enough.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:49.92,0:09:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}告诉那些来自德里的家伙..
Dialogue: 2,0:09:49.92,0:09:51.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Tell those p**ps from Delhi...
Dialogue: 3,0:09:53.00,0:09:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 我不会保持沉默太久-会没事的
Dialogue: 2,0:09:53.00,0:09:56.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- ...that I won't remain mum for long. - It'll be fine. It will all be fine.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:56.08,0:09:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}别担心，照顾好自己..
Dialogue: 2,0:09:56.08,0:09:58.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Don't worry. Take care of yourse...
Dialogue: 3,0:10:04.76,0:10:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}根据罪犯或被告的陈述..
Dialogue: 2,0:10:04.76,0:10:07.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Based on a statement made by a criminal or an accused...
Dialogue: 3,0:10:08.40,0:10:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}中央调查局即将开始调查这个国家的首相
Dialogue: 2,0:10:08.40,0:10:11.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...CBI will question the Prime Minister of this country...
Dialogue: 3,0:10:12.36,0:10:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这样合适吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:10:12.36,0:10:13.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...would that be appropriate?
Dialogue: 3,0:10:14.92,0:10:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}阁下，即使我们向马德文解释并阻止他..
Dialogue: 2,0:10:14.92,0:10:19.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Swami ji, even if we explain this to Madhavan and stop him...
Dialogue: 3,0:10:20.68,0:10:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这事也不会就此结束
Dialogue: 2,0:10:20.68,0:10:23.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...this won't end here.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:24.20,0:10:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}达斯，当一个问题有很多答案时... ..
Dialogue: 2,0:10:24.20,0:10:27.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Das, when a question has many answers...
Dialogue: 3,0:10:28.76,0:10:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}疑心总是集中在给出答案的人身上
Dialogue: 2,0:10:28.76,0:10:32.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...suspicion is always on the one giving the answers.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:33.76,0:10:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在这整个骗局中
Dialogue: 2,0:10:33.76,0:10:35.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[swami] 'And in this entire fraud, In this scam...'
Dialogue: 3,0:10:36.80,0:10:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“ ... 每个问题都应该只有一个答案”
Dialogue: 2,0:10:36.80,0:10:38.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...every question should lead to only one answer.'
Dialogue: 3,0:10:39.72,0:10:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈尔沙德 · 梅塔
Dialogue: 2,0:10:39.72,0:10:41.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad Mehta.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:43.48,0:10:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是唯一的答案
Dialogue: 2,0:10:43.48,0:10:44.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This is the one answer...
Dialogue: 3,0:10:45.04,0:10:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}公众和议会都会认可的
Dialogue: 2,0:10:45.04,0:10:47.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...that will be appreciated by both, the public and the parliament.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:51.00,0:10:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但我不知道马德文是否会同意
Dialogue: 2,0:10:51.00,0:10:55.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But I don't know if Madhavan will agree to this.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:56.60,0:10:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你俩谁是局长？
Dialogue: 2,0:10:56.60,0:10:59.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Are you the chief of CBI, or Madhavan?
Dialogue: 3,0:11:03.96,0:11:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还有一件重要的事
Dialogue: 2,0:11:03.96,0:11:05.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Swami] 'And one more important thing.'
Dialogue: 3,0:11:06.16,0:11:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那个记者... 苏切塔
Dialogue: 2,0:11:06.16,0:11:10.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That journalist... Sucheta... Sucheta Dalal.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:12.96,0:11:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}请你也照看一下她
Dialogue: 2,0:11:12.96,0:11:14.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Please keep an eye on her too.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:16.24,0:11:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}有人告诉她一些
Dialogue: 2,0:11:16.24,0:11:19.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}There is someone who is telling her things...
Dialogue: 3,0:11:20.56,0:11:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}她不应该知道的事情
Dialogue: 2,0:11:20.56,0:11:21.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...she shouldn't know.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:33.20,0:11:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我觉得有人在跟踪我们
Dialogue: 2,0:11:33.20,0:11:34.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I think someone is following us.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:09.56,0:12:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，我需要和你谈谈
Dialogue: 2,0:12:09.56,0:12:11.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, I need to talk to you.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:11.40,0:12:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好的
Dialogue: 2,0:12:11.40,0:12:12.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yes.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:14.08,0:12:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我的几个手下被派去监视一名记者，长官
Dialogue: 2,0:12:14.08,0:12:16.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}A few of my men have been asked to keep an eye on some journalist, sir.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:18.00,0:12:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 记者?-苏切塔
Dialogue: 2,0:12:18.00,0:12:19.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}-[Das] 'Journalist?' - Sucheta Dalal.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:19.56,0:12:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但这不是重点，先生，重点是..
Dialogue: 2,0:12:19.56,0:12:21.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But that's not the point, sir. The point is...
Dialogue: 3,0:12:22.24,0:12:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我的人力被用来做一些完全不必要的事情
Dialogue: 2,0:12:22.24,0:12:25.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...that my manpower is being used for something absolutely unnecessary and trivial.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:26.80,0:12:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你的人力？
Dialogue: 2,0:12:26.80,0:12:27.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Your manpower?
Dialogue: 3,0:12:29.68,0:12:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}马德文，让我们先把这件事弄清楚
Dialogue: 2,0:12:29.68,0:12:33.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Madhavan, let's get this thing very clear first.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:34.96,0:12:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们不是你的人
Dialogue: 2,0:12:34.96,0:12:37.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They are not your men.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:38.24,0:12:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们是中央调查局的警官
Dialogue: 2,0:12:38.24,0:12:39.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They are CBI officers.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:40.28,0:12:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我知道，长官
Dialogue: 2,0:12:40.28,0:12:41.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm aware of that, sir.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:42.04,0:12:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}经过这么多年的工作，我很清楚这一点
Dialogue: 2,0:12:42.04,0:12:44.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}After so many years in service, I'm well aware of that.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:46.16,0:12:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但重点是这些警官正在调查的案子..
Dialogue: 2,0:12:46.16,0:12:48.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But the point is, the case that these officers are working on...
Dialogue: 3,0:12:48.64,0:12:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 我是那个案子的负责人...-他们只是听从我的命令
Dialogue: 2,0:12:48.64,0:12:51.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- I'm the investigating officer of that case... - They're simply following my orders.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:52.84,0:12:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:12:52.84,0:12:53.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Okay?
Dialogue: 3,0:12:56.24,0:12:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好吧
Dialogue: 2,0:12:56.24,0:12:56.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Okay.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:59.36,0:13:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好吧
Dialogue: 2,0:12:59.36,0:13:00.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Okay.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:02.80,0:13:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果是这样的话，先生，我想再说一遍..
Dialogue: 2,0:13:02.80,0:13:04.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}In that case, sir, I want to repeat that...
Dialogue: 3,0:13:06.36,0:13:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}完全是浪费时间和资源
Dialogue: 2,0:13:06.36,0:13:08.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...it's a complete waste of time and resources.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:17.32,0:13:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}马德文
Dialogue: 2,0:13:17.32,0:13:18.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Madhavan...
Dialogue: 3,0:13:18.72,0:13:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 先生-你知道..
Dialogue: 2,0:13:18.72,0:13:19.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Sir. - You know...
Dialogue: 3,0:13:20.44,0:13:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我真的很欣赏你
Dialogue: 2,0:13:20.44,0:13:21.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I really like you.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:22.68,0:13:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我真的很欣赏你对这个案子的投入
Dialogue: 2,0:13:22.68,0:13:25.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I really like the way you're dedicated towards this case.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:25.52,0:13:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我也知道你是我们部门最好的
Dialogue: 2,0:13:25.52,0:13:29.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And I also know that you're the best in our department.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:29.96,0:13:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是请你... 请你试着理解
Dialogue: 2,0:13:29.96,0:13:33.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But please... Please try to understand.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:34.24,0:13:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我想让调查重回正轨
Dialogue: 2,0:13:34.24,0:13:38.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm trying to get this investigation back on the track.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:38.32,0:13:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}长官，调查从未偏离正轨
Dialogue: 2,0:13:38.32,0:13:39.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, the investigation never went off track.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:39.88,0:13:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 我不知道你在说什么-看在上帝的份上
Dialogue: 2,0:13:39.88,0:13:41.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- I don't know what you're talking about. - For God's sake, Madhavan.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:42.12,0:13:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是一个金融骗局！
Dialogue: 2,0:13:42.12,0:13:43.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This is a financial scam!
Dialogue: 3,0:13:47.24,0:13:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因为你的私人恩怨，你现在正试图
Dialogue: 2,0:13:47.24,0:13:49.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Because of your personal vendetta, you're unnecessarily trying...
Dialogue: 3,0:13:49.56,0:13:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}让这件事变得政治化
Dialogue: 2,0:13:49.56,0:13:51.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...to make this political.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:54.00,0:13:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}私人恩怨，先生？
Dialogue: 2,0:13:54.00,0:13:55.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Personal vendetta, sir?
Dialogue: 3,0:13:56.20,0:13:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}怎么个私人恩怨？
Dialogue: 2,0:13:56.20,0:13:59.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}How? How is it personal?
Dialogue: 3,0:14:00.12,0:14:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你不能把无辜的首相拖进这个烂摊子
Dialogue: 2,0:14:00.12,0:14:04.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You just cannot drag an innocent prime minister into this mess.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:05.92,0:14:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不要因为他令你不快，你就要像之前
Dialogue: 2,0:14:05.92,0:14:08.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Don't drag his name just because he was not happy with you...
Dialogue: 3,0:14:08.76,0:14:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}调查博福斯一样调查他
Dialogue: 2,0:14:08.76,0:14:10.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...the way you handled Bofors.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:11.56,0:14:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你有任何证据证明首相也在这个骗局中？
Dialogue: 2,0:14:11.56,0:14:14.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Do you have any proof against the PM in this scam?
Dialogue: 3,0:14:15.00,0:14:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}告诉我
Dialogue: 2,0:14:15.00,0:14:15.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Tell me.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:17.76,0:14:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你只是按照某个仆人告诉你的去做？
Dialogue: 2,0:14:17.76,0:14:19.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You're just going by what some lackey told you?
Dialogue: 3,0:14:21.00,0:14:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他正在试图转移这个案子，试着理解
Dialogue: 2,0:14:21.00,0:14:25.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He's trying to divert this case, try to understand.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:26.72,0:14:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你只需要关注哈沙德，仅此而已
Dialogue: 2,0:14:26.72,0:14:29.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You simply focus on Harshad, that's it.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:29.28,0:14:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生... 这么大的骗局..
Dialogue: 2,0:14:29.28,0:14:30.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir... such a huge scam...
Dialogue: 3,0:14:31.47,0:14:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}... 如此巨大的金融欺诈，我们现在都还没有具体数字
Dialogue: 2,0:14:31.48,0:14:34.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...such a huge financial fraud, that we're still only estimating the numbers...
Dialogue: 3,0:14:35.04,0:14:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你却想告诉我哈萨德是凭一己之力做到的！
Dialogue: 2,0:14:35.04,0:14:37.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And you're trying to tell me that Harshad pulled it off on his own!
Dialogue: 3,0:14:38.32,0:14:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没有任何支援吗，长官？
Dialogue: 2,0:14:38.32,0:14:39.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Without any support, sir?
Dialogue: 3,0:14:50.08,0:14:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我想从现在开始，这个案子应该由我来负责
Dialogue: 2,0:14:50.08,0:14:53.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I think from now, I should be taking charge of this case.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:54.92,0:14:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}-你说什么，先生?-是的
Dialogue: 2,0:14:54.92,0:14:56.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Sorry, sir? -[Das] 'Yes.'
Dialogue: 3,0:14:57.08,0:14:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我要接手这个案子
Dialogue: 2,0:14:57.08,0:14:58.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'I should be taking charge of this case.'
Dialogue: 3,0:15:00.96,0:15:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}马德文，我相信你会在中央调查局度过很好的职业生涯
Dialogue: 2,0:15:00.96,0:15:03.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Madhavan, I believe you have had a wonderful career in CBI.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:05.08,0:15:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不想让这个案子成为你和中央调查局的耻辱
Dialogue: 2,0:15:05.08,0:15:10.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I don't want this case to be a personal embarrassment for you and CBI, both.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:13.88,0:15:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我明白，长官
Dialogue: 2,0:15:13.88,0:15:14.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I get it, sir.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:18.92,0:15:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，我也不喜欢尴尬
Dialogue: 2,0:15:18.92,0:15:20.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, I am not very fond of being embarrassed either.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:22.44,0:15:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但我只想告诉你一件事
Dialogue: 2,0:15:22.44,0:15:23.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But I just want to tell you one thing.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:24.88,0:15:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你会很尴尬的，先生
Dialogue: 2,0:15:24.88,0:15:26.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Embarrassment is going to be your lot, sir.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:28.68,0:15:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}人们会叫你鹦鹉
Dialogue: 2,0:15:28.68,0:15:31.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}People will call you a parrot. A parrot.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:31.60,0:15:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你这是什么意思？
Dialogue: 2,0:15:31.60,0:15:33.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 3,0:15:33.68,0:15:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我是什么意思? 鹦鹉？
Dialogue: 2,0:15:33.68,0:15:34.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What do I mean? Parrot?
Dialogue: 3,0:15:37.72,0:15:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}长官，命令是从别的地方下来的
Dialogue: 2,0:15:37.72,0:15:39.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, the order has come from someplace else.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:40.08,0:15:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你只是在重复它们
Dialogue: 2,0:15:40.08,0:15:42.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You're just repeating them.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:44.00,0:15:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}鹦鹉经常重复它的主人说的任何话
Dialogue: 2,0:15:44.00,0:15:46.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And a parrot often repeats whatever its master speaks.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:48.72,0:15:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你是一只关在笼子里的鹦鹉，先生
Dialogue: 2,0:15:48.72,0:15:50.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You're a caged parrot, sir.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:53.24,0:15:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我会让事情简单一些，先生
Dialogue: 2,0:15:53.24,0:15:54.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'll make it easier for you, sir.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:55.08,0:15:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我要辞职
Dialogue: 2,0:15:55.08,0:15:55.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I will leave.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:57.52,0:15:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不是那种会听鹦鹉学舌的混蛋
Dialogue: 2,0:15:57.52,0:15:59.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm not the ass who will listen to a parrot.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:00.84,0:16:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我会把辞职信寄给你，祝您愉快，先生
Dialogue: 2,0:16:00.84,0:16:03.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'll send you my resignation. Have a good day, sir.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:05.64,0:16:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}听着
Dialogue: 2,0:16:05.64,0:16:06.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Listen, Madhavan...
Dialogue: 3,0:16:06.96,0:16:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}想想你应该跟媒体怎么说
Dialogue: 2,0:16:06.96,0:16:10.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Think about what you will tell the press, because that is going to be difficult.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:10.76,0:16:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你要怎么向他们解释..
Dialogue: 2,0:16:10.76,0:16:12.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}How are you going to explain to them...
Dialogue: 3,0:16:12.52,0:16:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}为什么这个案子的调查人员在调查过程中
Dialogue: 2,0:16:12.52,0:16:15.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...why the investigating officer of this case was compelled to leave...
Dialogue: 3,0:16:15.84,0:16:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}被迫离开？
Dialogue: 2,0:16:15.84,0:16:17.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...right in the middle of the investigation?
Dialogue: 3,0:16:18.36,0:16:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“你会说什么? ”
Dialogue: 2,0:16:18.36,0:16:19.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Madhavan] 'What will you say?'
Dialogue: 3,0:16:20.60,0:16:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}或者死记硬背主人给的答案，像鹦鹉一样重复
Dialogue: 2,0:16:20.60,0:16:24.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Or learn the master's answer by rote and repeat it like a parrot.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:26.24,0:16:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，还有一件事
Dialogue: 2,0:16:26.24,0:16:27.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And sir, one more thing.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:29.00,0:16:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}鹦鹉也被称为他的主人的声音
Dialogue: 2,0:16:29.00,0:16:30.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}A parrot is also referred to, as his masters voice.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:31.32,0:16:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以，如果媒体称你为他的主人，不要感到困惑
Dialogue: 2,0:16:31.32,0:16:33.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So if the press refers to you as his masters voice, don't get confused.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:33.88,0:16:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们还是在说你
Dialogue: 2,0:16:33.88,0:16:35.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They still mean you.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:37.08,0:16:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他的突然辞职会引发一些棘手的问题
Dialogue: 2,0:16:37.08,0:16:40.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[swami] 'His sudden resignation can raise some difficult questions.'
Dialogue: 3,0:16:41.60,0:16:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不，这不是问题
Dialogue: 2,0:16:41.60,0:16:42.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No. That's not a problem.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:43.76,0:16:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我会告诉媒体..
Dialogue: 2,0:16:43.76,0:16:45.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'll tell the press...
Dialogue: 3,0:16:46.04,0:16:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他很失望，因为他的升职没有通过
Dialogue: 2,0:16:46.04,0:16:48.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...that he was disappointed because his promotion didn't go through.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:49.80,0:16:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这就是他辞职的原因
Dialogue: 2,0:16:49.80,0:16:51.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That's why he resigned.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:53.08,0:16:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}有道理
Dialogue: 2,0:16:53.08,0:16:55.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[swami] 'That makes sense. Hari om.'
Dialogue: 3,0:17:02.16,0:17:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我给你开些药，定期服用
Dialogue: 2,0:17:02.16,0:17:05.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'll prescribe you some medicines, take them regularly.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:08.40,0:17:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}医生，这药有什么作用？
Dialogue: 2,0:17:08.40,0:17:09.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}How will medicines help, Doctor?
Dialogue: 3,0:17:11.08,0:17:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}看看这地方的状况
Dialogue: 2,0:17:11.08,0:17:12.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look at the state of this place.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:14.80,0:17:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“在这里呆了这么多天，我真是受够了”
Dialogue: 2,0:17:14.80,0:17:16.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] 'So many days in here have totally f****d me.'
Dialogue: 3,0:17:17.52,0:17:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你说过在这种情况下很容易获得保释
Dialogue: 2,0:17:17.52,0:17:19.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You had said it's easy to get bail in such cases.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:20.68,0:17:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}梅塔先生，别担心
Dialogue: 2,0:17:20.68,0:17:22.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Mr. Mehta, don't worry.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:22.88,0:17:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}调查局已经向特别法庭法官承诺..
Dialogue: 2,0:17:22.88,0:17:25.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}CBI has given an undertaking to the special court judge...
Dialogue: 3,0:17:25.80,0:17:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们的调查只能持续到7月30日
Dialogue: 2,0:17:25.80,0:17:28.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...that their investigation can only go on till 30th July.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:29.32,0:17:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 之后你就可以走了-你确定吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:17:29.32,0:17:31.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- You're free to go after that. - You're sure, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:17:31.44,0:17:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的，我已经确认过了
Dialogue: 2,0:17:31.44,0:17:33.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yes. I've seen the undertaking.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:41.24,0:17:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}很好
Dialogue: 2,0:17:41.24,0:17:42.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That's good.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:43.36,0:17:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我将在家里庆祝我的生日
Dialogue: 2,0:17:43.36,0:17:44.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'll celebrate my birthday at home.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:48.02,0:17:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我还从来没有..
Dialogue: 2,0:17:48.04,0:17:48.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I have never stayed...
Dialogue: 3,0:17:49.92,0:17:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}离家这么久
Dialogue: 2,0:17:49.92,0:17:51.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...away from home for so long.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:53.68,0:17:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}听着..
Dialogue: 2,0:17:53.68,0:17:54.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look...
Dialogue: 3,0:17:55.36,0:17:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们可以羁押哈沙德直到7月30日
Dialogue: 2,0:17:55.36,0:17:58.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We have Harshad's custody till the 30th of July.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:59.24,0:18:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但我们必须确保他..
Dialogue: 2,0:17:59.24,0:18:01.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But we have to make sure that we have him for...
Dialogue: 3,0:18:01.56,0:18:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}至少继续关押两个星期
Dialogue: 2,0:18:01.56,0:18:03.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...another fortnight at least.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:03.72,0:18:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}尽可能多申请FIRs
Dialogue: 2,0:18:03.72,0:18:06.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Do one thing, file as many FIRs as possible, against him.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:07.40,0:18:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好的，先生
Dialogue: 2,0:18:07.40,0:18:08.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[CBI officer] 'Okay, sir.'
Dialogue: 3,0:18:08.92,0:18:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}UCO 票据贴现案 PFC 交易..
Dialogue: 2,0:18:08.92,0:18:12.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The UCO bill discounting case, the PFC deal...
Dialogue: 3,0:18:13.20,0:18:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}都要提交FIRs
Dialogue: 2,0:18:13.20,0:18:14.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}File FIRs in all cases.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:16.04,0:18:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}然后去法院告诉他们我们正在调查15到16家银行..
Dialogue: 2,0:18:16.04,0:18:19.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Then go to the courts and tell them we are investigating 15 to 16 banks...
Dialogue: 3,0:18:19.32,0:18:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们需要哈尔沙德的帮助
Dialogue: 2,0:18:19.32,0:18:21.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...and we need Harshad in that connection.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:21.52,0:18:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我希望瓦里亚瓦法官会同意
Dialogue: 2,0:18:21.52,0:18:23.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I hope Justice Variava will agree.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:24.04,0:18:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ CBI 官员]“好的，先生，我们该怎么处理布尚？ ”
Dialogue: 2,0:18:24.04,0:18:26.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[CBI officer] 'Okay, sir. What do we do with Bhushan Bhatt?'
Dialogue: 3,0:18:27.72,0:18:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}布尚... 不会与哈尔沙德对抗
Dialogue: 2,0:18:27.72,0:18:32.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Bhushan Bhatt... will not go against Harshad.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:32.88,0:18:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他很忠诚，而且我们对他没什么意见
Dialogue: 2,0:18:32.88,0:18:35.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He's very loyal. And we don't have much against him.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:36.72,0:18:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以，不要在他身上浪费时间
Dialogue: 2,0:18:36.72,0:18:38.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, let's not waste time on him.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:40.56,0:18:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好的，先生
Dialogue: 2,0:18:40.56,0:18:41.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[CBI Officer] 'Okay, sir.'
Dialogue: 3,0:18:43.36,0:18:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不... 耐心点
Dialogue: 2,0:18:43.36,0:18:47.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No... Wait, have some patience.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:57.32,0:18:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈尔沙德？
Dialogue: 2,0:18:57.32,0:18:58.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad?
Dialogue: 3,0:19:01.16,0:19:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}调查局要求延长羁押时间
Dialogue: 2,0:19:01.16,0:19:02.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}CBI has asked for custody.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:04.12,0:19:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“还有15天”
Dialogue: 2,0:19:04.12,0:19:05.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Ashwin] 'Another 15 days.'
Dialogue: 3,0:19:07.28,0:19:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}接下来会发生什么，我们要等到13号才知道
Dialogue: 2,0:19:07.28,0:19:09.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What happens next, we'll only know on the 13th.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:11.52,0:19:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}已经两个月了，他们的审讯还没结束？
Dialogue: 2,0:19:11.52,0:19:14.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's been two months, and they are still not done with their interrogation?
Dialogue: 3,0:19:14.56,0:19:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们不会再把他关起来审问了
Dialogue: 2,0:19:14.56,0:19:16.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They are not holding him for interrogation anymore.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:16.92,0:19:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们是在找他麻烦
Dialogue: 2,0:19:16.92,0:19:17.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They're troubling him.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:18.48,0:19:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们正在向他施加压力，迫使他认罪
Dialogue: 2,0:19:18.48,0:19:20.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They are pressurising him to confess.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:21.64,0:19:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}希望他一个人背锅
Dialogue: 2,0:19:21.64,0:19:23.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They want him to admit that it's his mistake.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:27.52,0:19:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}嫂子，上面也有你的名字
Dialogue: 2,0:19:27.52,0:19:31.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Bhabhi, there's a notice in your name too.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:32.04,0:19:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我的名字？
Dialogue: 2,0:19:32.04,0:19:32.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}In my name?
Dialogue: 3,0:19:35.16,0:19:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的，这是你和哈沙德名下的税单
Dialogue: 2,0:19:35.16,0:19:40.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yes, it's a tax order in your and Harshad's names.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:41.28,0:19:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这张税单有多少钱？
Dialogue: 2,0:19:41.28,0:19:42.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}How much is the order for?
Dialogue: 3,0:19:42.96,0:19:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一千... 亿卢比
Dialogue: 2,0:19:42.96,0:19:45.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Ashwin] 'Ten thousand... crores.'
Dialogue: 3,0:19:49.72,0:19:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们调查过的所有银行..
Dialogue: 2,0:19:49.72,0:19:51.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}All the banks we investigated...
Dialogue: 3,0:19:52.40,0:19:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们的账簿上有一个共同的名字
Dialogue: 2,0:19:52.40,0:19:53.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...their books have one name in common.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:54.76,0:19:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈尔沙德 · 梅塔
Dialogue: 2,0:19:54.76,0:19:55.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad Mehta.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:57.64,0:19:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}迟早我们会发现..
Dialogue: 2,0:19:57.64,0:19:59.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sooner or later we are going to find out...
Dialogue: 3,0:20:00.16,0:20:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你是怎么独自完成这一切的
Dialogue: 2,0:20:00.16,0:20:02.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...how did you manage all of it on your own.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:04.04,0:20:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不过你最好告诉我们
Dialogue: 2,0:20:04.04,0:20:06.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But it'll be better if you tell us.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:07.32,0:20:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你在这些银行里贿赂了谁？
Dialogue: 2,0:20:07.32,0:20:10.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Whom did you bribe in these banks?
Dialogue: 3,0:20:10.40,0:20:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我没有贿赂任何一家银行的任何人
Dialogue: 2,0:20:10.40,0:20:12.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I haven't bribed anyone in any of these banks.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:13.24,0:20:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哦，是的! 你不用贿赂
Dialogue: 2,0:20:13.24,0:20:15.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Oh, yes! You don't bribe.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:17.00,0:20:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你为它创造了一个新的术语，叫什么来着..
Dialogue: 2,0:20:17.00,0:20:19.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You have coined a new term for it, what was it...
Dialogue: 3,0:20:20.76,0:20:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}银行家时代，对吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:20:20.76,0:20:22.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Bankerage, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:20:28.96,0:20:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你以为..
Dialogue: 2,0:20:28.96,0:20:29.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Did you think...
Dialogue: 3,0:20:31.04,0:20:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}中央调查局不懂你们的商业语言
Dialogue: 2,0:20:31.04,0:20:33.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...that because the CBI doesn't speak your financial language...
Dialogue: 3,0:20:33.60,0:20:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你就可以吹的天花乱坠？
Dialogue: 2,0:20:33.60,0:20:36.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...you can take us for a ride to the moon and back!?
Dialogue: 3,0:20:38.44,0:20:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“啊? ”
Dialogue: 2,0:20:38.44,0:20:39.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Das] 'Huh?'
Dialogue: 3,0:20:39.44,0:20:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你指挥了这么大的一场骗局..
Dialogue: 2,0:20:39.44,0:20:41.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You've conducted such a big fraud...
Dialogue: 3,0:20:42.12,0:20:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们请了一队会计师，却只能粗略估算涉案金额
Dialogue: 2,0:20:42.12,0:20:45.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...that we need an army of accountants just to get the estimates.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:46.80,0:20:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}而你却装作是你自己……
Dialogue: 2,0:20:46.80,0:20:48.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Das] 'And you're pretending that you pulled it off...'
Dialogue: 3,0:20:48.24,0:20:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}... 没有任何来自这些银行的内部支持
Dialogue: 2,0:20:48.24,0:20:50.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...without any internal support from these banks.'
Dialogue: 3,0:20:50.60,0:20:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我很清楚..
Dialogue: 2,0:20:50.60,0:20:52.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I know very well...
Dialogue: 3,0:20:52.84,0:20:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你在每家银行都有一个背景
Dialogue: 2,0:20:52.84,0:20:54.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...that you had a setting in every bank.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:55.12,0:20:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我没有任何背景
Dialogue: 2,0:20:55.12,0:20:56.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I didn't have any setting anywhere.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:57.84,0:21:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你所有的数字都是错的，完全不成比例
Dialogue: 2,0:20:57.84,0:21:00.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}All your numbers are wrong. It's all disproportionate.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:03.36,0:21:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不欠任何人一分钱，这是唯一的真相
Dialogue: 2,0:21:03.36,0:21:05.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I don't owe anyone a single penny and that's the only truth.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:09.60,0:21:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈沙德，你让你的生活越来越艰难了
Dialogue: 2,0:21:09.60,0:21:13.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad, you're making your life more and more difficult.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:15.36,0:21:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“你会烂在监狱里的”
Dialogue: 2,0:21:15.36,0:21:17.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Das] 'Jail will become your permanent address.'
Dialogue: 3,0:21:43.32,0:21:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是沟通的方式吗? 你可以打电话给我..
Dialogue: 2,0:21:43.32,0:21:46.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Is this a way to communicate? You could have phoned me...
Dialogue: 3,0:21:46.04,0:21:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我承认这是错误的方式，所以我在便条上道歉
Dialogue: 2,0:21:46.04,0:21:50.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I admit it's the wrong way, Suchetaji. That's why I apologised on the note.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:50.92,0:21:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但我别无选择
Dialogue: 2,0:21:50.92,0:21:52.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But I didn't have a choice.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:53.32,0:21:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}中央调查局全天候监视着我们
Dialogue: 2,0:21:53.32,0:21:55.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The CBI has eyes on us 24/7.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:56.32,0:21:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们可能在窃听我们的电话..
Dialogue: 2,0:21:56.32,0:21:58.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They might be tapping our phones...
Dialogue: 3,0:21:58.56,0:22:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}也许你的电话也被监听了
Dialogue: 2,0:21:58.56,0:22:00.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...maybe your phone is also being tapped.
Dialogue: 3,0:22:00.76,0:22:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}毕竟，你和这个案子也有关系
Dialogue: 2,0:22:00.76,0:22:02.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}After all, you are connected with this case too...
Dialogue: 3,0:22:03.12,0:22:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}政府呢? 他们把我们当恐怖分子对待
Dialogue: 2,0:22:03.12,0:22:06.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...and the government? They are treating us like terrorists.
Dialogue: 3,0:22:07.52,0:22:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我害怕加州调查局会杀了我兄弟哈沙德
Dialogue: 2,0:22:07.52,0:22:10.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm scared that CBI might kill my brother Harshad.
Dialogue: 3,0:22:10.64,0:22:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他情况很不好，我得告诉别人..
Dialogue: 2,0:22:10.64,0:22:13.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He's in a bad state. I had to tell someone...
Dialogue: 3,0:22:13.00,0:22:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}为什么是我? 你可以去找其他记者？
Dialogue: 2,0:22:13.00,0:22:16.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Why me? You could have gone to any other journalist?
Dialogue: 3,0:22:17.24,0:22:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 我怕我会失去我的兄弟...-你为什么要告诉我这些？
Dialogue: 2,0:22:17.24,0:22:20.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- I'm scared I might lose my brother... - Why are you telling me this?
Dialogue: 3,0:22:20.32,0:22:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你担心你弟弟? 可是那些人怎么办..
Dialogue: 2,0:22:20.32,0:22:22.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You're worried about your brother? What about those people...
Dialogue: 3,0:22:22.72,0:22:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那些一生的积蓄和家庭都被你哥哥毁了的人怎么办？
Dialogue: 2,0:22:22.72,0:22:26.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...whose life's savings and families have been ruined by your brother?
Dialogue: 3,0:22:27.24,0:22:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}把这些人的故事写出来不是更好吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:22:27.24,0:22:28.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Won't it be better to write about them?
Dialogue: 3,0:22:29.64,0:22:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}求你了，苏切塔..
Dialogue: 2,0:22:29.64,0:22:31.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Please, Suchetaji...
Dialogue: 3,0:22:45.04,0:22:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}‘开门，是我’
Dialogue: 2,0:22:45.04,0:22:46.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Rahil's wife] 'Open the door, it's me.'
Dialogue: 3,0:22:48.56,0:22:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我一个人在外面
Dialogue: 2,0:22:48.56,0:22:49.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'I'm alone out here.'
Dialogue: 3,0:22:53.44,0:22:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}快进来
Dialogue: 2,0:22:53.44,0:22:54.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Come in quickly.
Dialogue: 3,0:22:54.48,0:22:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你在干什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:22:54.48,0:22:55.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 3,0:22:57.44,0:22:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不是叫你从外面锁门吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:22:57.44,0:22:58.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Didn't I ask you to lock the door from outside?
Dialogue: 3,0:23:02.04,0:23:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们还要被锁在里面多久？
Dialogue: 2,0:23:02.04,0:23:03.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}How much longer will we stay locked in?
Dialogue: 3,0:23:03.92,0:23:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我该怎么办? 告诉我
Dialogue: 2,0:23:03.92,0:23:06.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What should I do? Tell me.
Dialogue: 3,0:23:06.40,0:23:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}每次我一出门，他们就来找我要钱
Dialogue: 2,0:23:06.40,0:23:09.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Every time I step out, they harass me for money.
Dialogue: 3,0:23:13.04,0:23:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}上次他们威胁要杀了我
Dialogue: 2,0:23:13.04,0:23:15.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Last time, they threatened to kill me.
Dialogue: 3,0:23:15.60,0:23:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不，我知道他们不会真的杀我
Dialogue: 2,0:23:15.60,0:23:19.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No, I know, that they won't kill me.
Dialogue: 3,0:23:19.88,0:23:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们会把我交给警察
Dialogue: 2,0:23:19.88,0:23:21.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They'll hand me over to the police.
Dialogue: 3,0:23:21.04,0:23:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}警察还没有放哈沙德走，他们会对我做什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:23:21.04,0:23:23.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The police didn't let Harshad go, what will they do to me?
Dialogue: 3,0:23:24.44,0:23:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不，什么都不会发生
Dialogue: 2,0:23:24.44,0:23:26.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No, nothing will happen.
Dialogue: 3,0:23:26.40,0:23:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 一切都结束了-不
Dialogue: 2,0:23:26.40,0:23:27.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Everything is over. - No.
Dialogue: 3,0:23:27.76,0:23:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 不，真的，一切都结束了-不
Dialogue: 2,0:23:27.76,0:23:29.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- No, really, everything is over. - No.
Dialogue: 3,0:23:29.80,0:23:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你说得对，我不能再这样生活下去了
Dialogue: 2,0:23:29.80,0:23:33.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You're right. I won't be able to live like this.
Dialogue: 3,0:23:33.44,0:23:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 我不能这样活着，躲在恐惧中-拉希尔..
Dialogue: 2,0:23:33.44,0:23:37.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- I can't live like this, hiding in fear. - Rahil...
Dialogue: 3,0:23:47.80,0:23:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[法官]“你确定你已经完成了所有的调查吗? ”
Dialogue: 2,0:23:47.80,0:23:49.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Judge] 'Are you sure you have completed all your investigations?'
Dialogue: 3,0:23:50.24,0:23:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的，先生
Dialogue: 2,0:23:50.24,0:23:51.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[CBI Attorney] 'Yes, sir.'
Dialogue: 3,0:23:51.20,0:23:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好了，梅塔先生，你的保释现在被批准了
Dialogue: 2,0:23:51.20,0:23:53.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Judge] 'Okay, Mr. Mehta, your bail is sanctioned now.'
Dialogue: 3,0:24:07.32,0:24:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}别担心，好吗? 和乔蒂出去玩几天
Dialogue: 2,0:24:07.32,0:24:11.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Ashwin] 'Don't worry, okay? Go out for a few days with Jyoti.'
Dialogue: 3,0:24:11.88,0:24:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}梅塔先生我们是执法局的
Dialogue: 2,0:24:11.88,0:24:14.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Mr. Mehta, we are from the Enforcement Directorate.
Dialogue: 3,0:24:15.12,0:24:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们以违反《外汇管理法》逮捕你
Dialogue: 2,0:24:15.12,0:24:18.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We are arresting you for breaking the Foreign Exchange Regulation Act...
Dialogue: 3,0:24:18.88,0:24:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}根据第35条和第62条
Dialogue: 2,0:24:18.88,0:24:20.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...under section 35 and 62.
Dialogue: 3,0:24:21.16,0:24:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}-请...-你有搜查令吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:24:21.16,0:24:22.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- So please... - Do you have a warrant?
Dialogue: 3,0:24:22.72,0:24:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 逮捕他-逮捕令？
Dialogue: 2,0:24:22.72,0:24:23.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Arrest him. - Warrant?
Dialogue: 3,0:24:24.32,0:24:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}给我们看文件，邦主律师，和他们谈谈
Dialogue: 2,0:24:24.32,0:24:27.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Show us the papers. Lawyer saheb, talk to them.
Dialogue: 3,0:24:28.20,0:24:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你是说你在任何一家瑞士银行都没有账户？
Dialogue: 2,0:24:28.20,0:24:30.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So you're saying you don't have any account in any swiss bank?
Dialogue: 3,0:24:30.96,0:24:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我没有
Dialogue: 2,0:24:30.96,0:24:31.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No, I don't.
Dialogue: 3,0:24:32.08,0:24:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那么，你怎么把钱转移到国外呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:24:32.08,0:24:34.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So then, how do you transfer your money abroad?
Dialogue: 3,0:24:36.04,0:24:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 通过洗钱?-什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:24:36.04,0:24:37.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- By laundering money? - What?
Dialogue: 3,0:24:38.48,0:24:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们可以在几分钟内获得你们接线员的详细资料
Dialogue: 2,0:24:38.48,0:24:42.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We can get the details of your operator in minutes.
Dialogue: 3,0:24:43.04,0:24:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我没有任何人为我洗钱
Dialogue: 2,0:24:43.04,0:24:44.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I don't have anybody who launders money for me.
Dialogue: 3,0:24:44.76,0:24:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 所以你没有接线员?-没有
Dialogue: 2,0:24:44.76,0:24:47.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- So you don't have an operator? - No, I don't.
Dialogue: 3,0:24:47.36,0:24:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那么，莫汉 · 拉尔是谁呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:24:47.36,0:24:48.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Who is this Mohan Lal, then?
Dialogue: 3,0:24:49.44,0:24:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你的一个前雇员用了他的名字
Dialogue: 2,0:24:49.44,0:24:51.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}One of your ex-employees took his name...
Dialogue: 3,0:24:52.44,0:24:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你不是在开市那天派他去的吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:24:52.44,0:24:55.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...didn't you send him there on the day of the market opening?
Dialogue: 3,0:24:56.28,0:24:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}莫汉拉尔 · 米萨瓦拉
Dialogue: 2,0:24:56.28,0:24:57.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Mohanlal S. Mithaiwala.
Dialogue: 3,0:25:01.20,0:25:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他是个糖果师，不是洗钱的
Dialogue: 2,0:25:01.20,0:25:03.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He is a confectioner. Not a money launderer.
Dialogue: 3,0:25:07.32,0:25:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}很明显，你的消息来源有问题
Dialogue: 2,0:25:07.32,0:25:09.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's so clear that your source is deaf.
Dialogue: 3,0:25:27.92,0:25:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“我们不能再继续关押哈萨德了”
Dialogue: 2,0:25:27.92,0:25:32.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Das] 'We can't keep Harshad locked up anymore.'
Dialogue: 3,0:25:33.64,0:25:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他已经被执法局拘留五周了
Dialogue: 2,0:25:33.64,0:25:35.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'He's been in ED's custody for five weeks.'
Dialogue: 3,0:25:35.92,0:25:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}回答法庭和媒体的问题可能会很困难
Dialogue: 2,0:25:35.92,0:25:38.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It can get tough to answer the court and the media.
Dialogue: 3,0:25:39.72,0:25:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所有人都被保释了，即使是 SBI 的人
Dialogue: 2,0:25:39.72,0:25:42.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Everyone has been released on bail. Even the SBI people.
Dialogue: 3,0:25:43.04,0:25:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们还能把哈萨德关多久？
Dialogue: 2,0:25:43.04,0:25:44.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...How much longer can we keep Harshad locked up?
Dialogue: 3,0:25:46.24,0:25:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ Swami ]“那就让他走吧”
Dialogue: 2,0:25:46.24,0:25:47.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Swami] 'Let him go then.'
Dialogue: 3,0:25:48.36,0:25:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果你不能再继续关押，那就这样吧... ..
Dialogue: 2,0:25:48.36,0:25:51.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'If you can't lock him up physically, so be it...'
Dialogue: 3,0:25:51.96,0:25:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}至少，你可以在精神上束缚住他
Dialogue: 2,0:25:51.96,0:25:54.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...at least, you can tie him down mentally.'
Dialogue: 3,0:25:54.84,0:25:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“提醒他不要散布有关首相的谣言”
Dialogue: 2,0:25:54.84,0:25:59.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Remind him not to spread rumours about the Prime Minister.'
Dialogue: 3,0:26:00.72,0:26:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果他再犯这样的错误..
Dialogue: 2,0:26:00.72,0:26:02.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'And if he makes such a mistake again...'
Dialogue: 3,0:26:02.96,0:26:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}’ ... 他将被控告更多的罪行，更多的案件... ’
Dialogue: 2,0:26:02.96,0:26:06.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...he will be accused for so many more crimes in so many more cases...'
Dialogue: 3,0:26:07.24,0:26:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他会在监狱里呆上10到15年
Dialogue: 2,0:26:07.24,0:26:09.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...that he'll spend 10 to 15 years in jail.'
Dialogue: 3,0:26:10.12,0:26:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 好的 Swami 先生
Dialogue: 2,0:26:10.12,0:26:11.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Okay, Swami ji. - Hari Om.
Dialogue: 3,0:26:34.40,0:26:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“哈沙德大哥.. ... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:26:34.40,0:26:35.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[crowd] 'Harshad Bhai...'
Dialogue: 3,0:26:35.76,0:26:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈沙德大哥
Dialogue: 2,0:26:35.76,0:26:38.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Harshad Bhai...'
Dialogue: 3,0:26:38.48,0:26:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈沙德大哥
Dialogue: 2,0:26:38.48,0:26:41.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Harshad Bhai...'
Dialogue: 3,0:26:43.28,0:26:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈沙德大哥
Dialogue: 2,0:26:43.28,0:26:46.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Harshad Bhai...'
Dialogue: 3,0:27:07.64,0:27:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈沙德大哥
Dialogue: 2,0:27:07.64,0:27:09.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad Bhai...
Dialogue: 3,0:27:11.48,0:27:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈沙德大哥！
Dialogue: 2,0:27:11.48,0:27:12.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad Bhai!
Dialogue: 3,0:27:15.72,0:27:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈沙德大哥！
Dialogue: 2,0:27:15.72,0:27:17.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad Bhai!
Dialogue: 3,0:27:29.96,0:27:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我的儿子！
Dialogue: 2,0:27:29.96,0:27:31.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}My son!
Dialogue: 3,0:27:33.52,0:27:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}让我驱散那恶毒的眼睛
Dialogue: 2,0:27:33.52,0:27:35.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Let me ward off the evil eye.
Dialogue: 3,0:27:37.24,0:27:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}小混蛋！
Dialogue: 2,0:27:37.24,0:27:38.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Rascals!
Dialogue: 3,0:27:40.47,0:27:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你变得这么虚弱..
Dialogue: 2,0:27:40.52,0:27:42.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}How weak you've become...
Dialogue: 3,0:27:43.28,0:27:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在那里睡不着觉，对不对？
Dialogue: 2,0:27:43.28,0:27:44.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You couldn't sleep there, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:27:45.64,0:27:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我在新闻上看到你用鞋子当枕头睡在地板上..
Dialogue: 2,0:27:45.64,0:27:49.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I read in the news that you slept on the floor using shoes as a pillow...
Dialogue: 3,0:27:49.08,0:27:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 哦，妈咪!-别说了，妈妈..
Dialogue: 2,0:27:49.08,0:27:50.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Oh, Mummy! - Stop it, Mummy...
Dialogue: 3,0:27:52.28,0:27:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 去吃点东西然后睡觉-好的
Dialogue: 2,0:27:52.28,0:27:56.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Go, eat something and go to sleep. - Yes.
Dialogue: 3,0:27:57.36,0:27:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我做了拉普西麦片粥
Dialogue: 2,0:27:57.36,0:27:58.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I've made lapsi. porridge
Dialogue: 3,0:28:00.68,0:28:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}妈妈，请告诉我她没有做茄子泥和茄子粥
Dialogue: 2,0:28:00.68,0:28:03.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Mummy, please tell me she didn't make an eggplant mash with lapsi. brinjal/ porridge
Dialogue: 3,0:28:04.56,0:28:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因为已经被我碾碎了
Dialogue: 2,0:28:04.56,0:28:06.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Because I have already been mashed.
Dialogue: 3,0:28:08.36,0:28:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他还是那么幽默
Dialogue: 2,0:28:08.36,0:28:09.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He hasn't lost his humour.
Dialogue: 3,0:28:11.04,0:28:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}去吧，乔蒂
Dialogue: 2,0:28:11.04,0:28:11.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Go, Jyoti.
Dialogue: 3,0:28:19.84,0:28:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}很多水果，梅塔先生
Dialogue: 2,0:28:19.84,0:28:21.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Lots of fruits, Mr. Mehta.'
Dialogue: 3,0:28:22.00,0:28:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你变得非常注重健康了
Dialogue: 2,0:28:22.00,0:28:23.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'You've become quite health conscious.'
Dialogue: 3,0:28:27.44,0:28:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}橘子，最近我很喜欢橘子
Dialogue: 2,0:28:27.44,0:28:30.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Oranges. These days I'm loving oranges.
Dialogue: 3,0:28:34.16,0:28:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你在监狱里吃过饭吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:28:34.16,0:28:35.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Have you ever had prison food?
Dialogue: 3,0:28:38.20,0:28:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你喝过监狱的水吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:28:38.20,0:28:39.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Have you ever had water there?
Dialogue: 3,0:28:40.32,0:28:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你见过监狱里面什么样吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:28:40.32,0:28:41.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Have you ever seen the inside of a jail?
Dialogue: 3,0:28:45.28,0:28:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}即使是我的敌人，我也不希望他们经历这些
Dialogue: 2,0:28:45.28,0:28:47.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I don't wish that even for my enemy.
Dialogue: 3,0:28:50.08,0:28:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我满怀信心地走了进去
Dialogue: 2,0:28:50.08,0:28:51.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I went in with such pride.
Dialogue: 3,0:28:52.88,0:28:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但四个月后..
Dialogue: 2,0:28:52.88,0:28:54.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But in four months...
Dialogue: 3,0:28:55.52,0:28:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我已经完全泄气了
Dialogue: 2,0:28:55.52,0:28:56.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I've been completely deflated.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:00.24,0:29:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}然后我明白了..
Dialogue: 2,0:29:00.24,0:29:01.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And then I've understood...
Dialogue: 3,0:29:02.96,0:29:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}”健康就是财富”的意思
Dialogue: 2,0:29:02.96,0:29:05.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...what "Health is wealth" means.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:08.00,0:29:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我也明白..
Dialogue: 2,0:29:08.00,0:29:09.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And I've also understood...
Dialogue: 3,0:29:11.28,0:29:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}关键时刻还是要靠自己
Dialogue: 2,0:29:11.28,0:29:13.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...that I will only have to help myself.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:16.08,0:29:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不是这样的
Dialogue: 2,0:29:16.08,0:29:17.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That's not true.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:18.16,0:29:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你的朋友在你需要的时候帮助了你
Dialogue: 2,0:29:18.16,0:29:19.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Your friends helped you when you needed it.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:22.12,0:29:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈沙德，你来德里却不告诉我？
Dialogue: 2,0:29:22.12,0:29:25.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad, you came to Delhi and didn't tell me?
Dialogue: 3,0:29:26.08,0:29:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你应该先打个电话
Dialogue: 2,0:29:26.08,0:29:27.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You could've called.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:28.28,0:29:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我从别人那里得知你的到来，真是奇怪
Dialogue: 2,0:29:28.28,0:29:30.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's strange that I get to know from others about your arrival.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:32.84,0:29:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你只告诉你的朋友
Dialogue: 2,0:29:32.84,0:29:34.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You only inform your friends about your plans.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:35.60,0:29:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}朋友
Dialogue: 2,0:29:35.60,0:29:36.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Friends.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:38.08,0:29:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 请吃点东西-谢谢
Dialogue: 2,0:29:38.08,0:29:40.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Please have something. - Thank you. Thank you.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:40.84,0:29:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}补钙，你应该多吃点
Dialogue: 2,0:29:40.84,0:29:42.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's good for calcium, you should have.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:44.96,0:29:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你在JPC的朋友也找过我
Dialogue: 2,0:29:44.96,0:29:47.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Your friends from the JPC have also summoned me.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:50.76,0:29:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}真是巧啊..
Dialogue: 2,0:29:50.76,0:29:51.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And what a coincidence...
Dialogue: 3,0:29:53.04,0:29:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你在同一时间想起了我
Dialogue: 2,0:29:53.04,0:29:55.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You thought of me at the exact same time.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:58.64,0:30:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在我出现在议会委员会之前，你突然出现了
Dialogue: 2,0:29:58.64,0:30:01.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Before I appear at the parliamentary committee, you appeared here.
Dialogue: 3,0:30:03.36,0:30:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我知道，在JPC
Dialogue: 2,0:30:03.36,0:30:06.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I realise. At the JPC...
Dialogue: 3,0:30:07.56,0:30:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果出现了首相的名字
Dialogue: 2,0:30:07.56,0:30:10.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...if any names pop up, the PM...
Dialogue: 3,0:30:11.28,0:30:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}斯瓦米先生就有麻烦了
Dialogue: 2,0:30:11.28,0:30:13.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...and Swami ji will be in trouble.
Dialogue: 3,0:30:16.16,0:30:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}告诉我一些事情
Dialogue: 2,0:30:16.16,0:30:17.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] 'Tell me something.'
Dialogue: 3,0:30:18.32,0:30:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们是担心我还是担心他们自己？
Dialogue: 2,0:30:18.32,0:30:19.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Are they worried for me or themselves?
Dialogue: 3,0:30:22.32,0:30:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈沙德，现在委员会已经有很多名字了
Dialogue: 2,0:30:22.32,0:30:26.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad, a lot of names have already been taken before the JPC.
Dialogue: 3,0:30:27.96,0:30:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不应该有更多的名字
Dialogue: 2,0:30:27.96,0:30:29.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}There shouldn't be any more names.
Dialogue: 3,0:30:31.60,0:30:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这对大家都有好处
Dialogue: 2,0:30:31.60,0:30:33.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's in everybody's best interest.
Dialogue: 3,0:30:34.92,0:30:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}尤其是对你
Dialogue: 2,0:30:34.92,0:30:36.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Especially yours.
Dialogue: 3,0:30:44.16,0:30:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}对
Dialogue: 2,0:30:44.16,0:30:44.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Right.
Dialogue: 3,0:30:49.08,0:30:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不会说出任何名字
Dialogue: 2,0:30:49.08,0:30:50.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I won't take any names.
Dialogue: 3,0:30:53.00,0:30:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}只要你一直保护我
Dialogue: 2,0:30:53.00,0:30:54.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}As long as you keep protecting me.
Dialogue: 3,0:30:56.12,0:30:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}当然，哈尔沙德
Dialogue: 2,0:30:56.12,0:30:57.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Of course, Harshad.
Dialogue: 3,0:30:58.64,0:31:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好吧，我就说你来这里想说的
Dialogue: 2,0:30:58.64,0:31:00.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Okay, I'll say what you came here to say.
Dialogue: 3,0:31:02.88,0:31:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不会提到首相
Dialogue: 2,0:31:02.88,0:31:04.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I won't mention the Prime Minister.
Dialogue: 3,0:31:11.92,0:31:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你看，在这些所谓的启示之后..
Dialogue: 2,0:31:11.92,0:31:14.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You see, after these so-called revelations...
Dialogue: 3,0:31:15.40,0:31:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}很多人都给这个骗局起了不同的名字
Dialogue: 2,0:31:15.40,0:31:17.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...various people have given various names to the scam.
Dialogue: 3,0:31:18.52,0:31:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}最初，它被称为股票骗局
Dialogue: 2,0:31:18.52,0:31:20.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Initially, it was called the stock scam.
Dialogue: 3,0:31:21.12,0:31:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}经纪人不喜欢这样，所以他们称之为银行骗局
Dialogue: 2,0:31:21.12,0:31:23.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Brokers didn't like it so they called it the bank scam.
Dialogue: 3,0:31:24.28,0:31:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但如果要我说
Dialogue: 2,0:31:24.28,0:31:25.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But I will tell you what it is.
Dialogue: 3,0:31:26.48,0:31:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这就是花旗的骗局
Dialogue: 2,0:31:26.48,0:31:27.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It is the Citi scam.
Dialogue: 3,0:31:35.68,0:31:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}花旗银行是这个系统中所有非法活动的集中地
Dialogue: 2,0:31:35.68,0:31:38.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Citibank is the beehive of all the illegal activities in the system.
Dialogue: 3,0:31:44.52,0:31:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}让我们看看印度的货币市场
Dialogue: 2,0:31:44.52,0:31:46.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Let's just look at our Indian money markets.
Dialogue: 3,0:31:47.56,0:31:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在印度货币市场，像花旗银行这样的外国银行可以随心所欲地管理资金
Dialogue: 2,0:31:47.56,0:31:50.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}In the Indian money market, foreign banks like Citibank rule as they wish.
Dialogue: 3,0:31:51.60,0:31:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}而且他们还赚了一大笔钱
Dialogue: 2,0:31:51.60,0:31:53.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And they mint a ton of money.
Dialogue: 3,0:31:56.40,0:31:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}花旗银行有财力
Dialogue: 2,0:31:56.40,0:31:57.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Citibank has all the money...
Dialogue: 3,0:31:58.44,0:32:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}去购买所有新发行的政府债券
Dialogue: 2,0:31:58.44,0:32:00.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...to buy every new issue of every government bonds.
Dialogue: 3,0:32:02.48,0:32:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们在市场上占有最大的份额
Dialogue: 2,0:32:02.48,0:32:03.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They have the lion's share in the market.
Dialogue: 3,0:32:05.36,0:32:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因此，一旦他们垄断了所有的证券，所有散户都将任由他们摆布
Dialogue: 2,0:32:05.36,0:32:08.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So once they corner all the securities, all the small players are at their mercy.
Dialogue: 3,0:32:12.16,0:32:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这还不是全部
Dialogue: 2,0:32:12.16,0:32:13.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And that's not all.
Dialogue: 3,0:32:14.56,0:32:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}花旗银行确保..
Dialogue: 2,0:32:14.56,0:32:15.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Citibank makes sure...
Dialogue: 3,0:32:16.36,0:32:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}它在市场上保持着支配地位
Dialogue: 2,0:32:16.36,0:32:18.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...that it maintains a dominant position in the market.
Dialogue: 3,0:32:19.08,0:32:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们是怎么做到的呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:32:19.08,0:32:20.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And how do they do it?
Dialogue: 3,0:32:22.60,0:32:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}利用系统中的漏洞..
Dialogue: 2,0:32:22.60,0:32:24.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}By exploiting the loopholes in the system...
Dialogue: 3,0:32:25.40,0:32:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}通过违反 RBI 的指导方针..
Dialogue: 2,0:32:25.40,0:32:27.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}By violating RBI guidelines...
Dialogue: 3,0:32:28.68,0:32:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}通过影响德里的政策制定
Dialogue: 2,0:32:28.68,0:32:30.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...and by influencing policy-making in Delhi...
Dialogue: 3,0:32:30.96,0:32:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}通过他们强大的顾问委员会
Dialogue: 2,0:32:30.96,0:32:32.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...through their powerful advisory boards.
Dialogue: 3,0:32:37.88,0:32:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}超过80% 的交易涉及复杂的财团
Dialogue: 2,0:32:37.88,0:32:41.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}More than 80 percent transactions have sophisticated syndicates involved.
Dialogue: 3,0:32:41.68,0:32:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们不让外人进入
Dialogue: 2,0:32:41.68,0:32:43.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They don't let outsiders enter.
Dialogue: 3,0:32:45.20,0:32:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们可以很容易地利用..
Dialogue: 2,0:32:45.20,0:32:46.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And they can easily exploit...
Dialogue: 3,0:32:47.36,0:32:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}缓慢而无知的印度银行系统
Dialogue: 2,0:32:47.36,0:32:49.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...the slow and ignorant Indian banking system.
Dialogue: 3,0:32:53.32,0:32:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}甚至没有人理解这一点
Dialogue: 2,0:32:53.32,0:32:54.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No one even understands this.
Dialogue: 3,0:32:57.08,0:32:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}很少有像苏切塔 · 达拉尔这样的记者提出这个问题
Dialogue: 2,0:32:57.08,0:32:59.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Very few journalists like Sucheta Dalal have brought it out.
Dialogue: 3,0:33:04.16,0:33:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我愿意帮忙
Dialogue: 2,0:33:04.16,0:33:05.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm willing to help.
Dialogue: 3,0:33:06.64,0:33:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}整个真相都会大白于天下
Dialogue: 2,0:33:06.64,0:33:08.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The whole truth will be out.
Dialogue: 3,0:33:09.24,0:33:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我已经准备好和所有的调查机构合作了
Dialogue: 2,0:33:09.24,0:33:11.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm ready to cooperate with all the investigative agencies.
Dialogue: 3,0:33:13.56,0:33:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但前提是免除我所有的罪名
Dialogue: 2,0:33:13.56,0:33:16.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But only if I'm exonerated from all the charges.
Dialogue: 3,0:33:31.40,0:33:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果我是你的话..
Dialogue: 2,0:33:31.40,0:33:33.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If I was in your shoes...
Dialogue: 3,0:33:35.76,0:33:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}... 首先，我会调查 PMS 交易
Dialogue: 2,0:33:35.76,0:33:38.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...to start with, I'd be looking into PMS deals.
Dialogue: 3,0:33:40.72,0:33:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}花旗银行的
Dialogue: 2,0:33:40.72,0:33:43.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}PMS. Portfolio management services...
Dialogue: 3,0:33:45.00,0:33:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}投资组合管理服务
Dialogue: 2,0:33:45.00,0:33:45.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...of Citibank.
Dialogue: 3,0:33:47.48,0:33:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一旦你开始调查，你就会明白为什么花旗银行是主脑... ..
Dialogue: 2,0:33:47.48,0:33:50.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Once you do that you'll realise why Citibank is the kingpin...
Dialogue: 3,0:33:50.04,0:33:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}印度所有可疑的 PMS 交易
Dialogue: 2,0:33:50.04,0:33:52.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...of all the dubious PMS deals in India.
Dialogue: 3,0:33:56.36,0:33:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}特亚吉先生，我不想浪费时间
Dialogue: 2,0:33:56.36,0:33:59.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Mr. Tyagi, I will not waste time.
Dialogue: 3,0:34:01.44,0:34:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}让我们开门见山吧
Dialogue: 2,0:34:01.44,0:34:02.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Let us get straight to the point.
Dialogue: 3,0:34:05.02,0:34:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在对贵行有严重的指控
Dialogue: 2,0:34:05.04,0:34:07.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}There are severe allegations against your bank.
Dialogue: 3,0:34:10.32,0:34:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}什么样的指控？
Dialogue: 2,0:34:10.32,0:34:11.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What kind of allegations?
Dialogue: 3,0:34:12.00,0:34:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}贵行和其他银行一样，也有违规行为
Dialogue: 2,0:34:12.00,0:34:16.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Your bank is involved in irregularities like other banks.
Dialogue: 3,0:34:16.48,0:34:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}比如说？
Dialogue: 2,0:34:16.48,0:34:17.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}For example?
Dialogue: 3,0:34:17.44,0:34:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}关于PMS违规行为，例如..
Dialogue: 2,0:34:17.44,0:34:20.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Irregularities regarding PMS, for example...
Dialogue: 3,0:34:21.40,0:34:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你可以翻我们所有的账簿，我没什么好隐瞒的
Dialogue: 2,0:34:21.40,0:34:24.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You can go through all our books. I have nothing to hide.
Dialogue: 3,0:34:25.40,0:34:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}事实上，我可以亲自帮助你更好地理解我的账簿
Dialogue: 2,0:34:25.40,0:34:29.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}In fact, I can personally assist you to get a better understanding of my books.
Dialogue: 3,0:34:30.48,0:34:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们所有的交易，每一笔交易，都严格按照..
Dialogue: 2,0:34:30.48,0:34:33.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}All our deals, every single one of them, are in strict accordance...
Dialogue: 3,0:34:33.48,0:34:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}印度储备银行制定的指导方针
Dialogue: 2,0:34:33.48,0:34:35.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...with the guidelines set by the Reserve bank of India.
Dialogue: 3,0:34:36.68,0:34:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们从来没有藐视过任何一条规则
Dialogue: 2,0:34:36.68,0:34:38.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We have never flouted a single rule.
Dialogue: 3,0:34:39.88,0:34:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你应该知道，我们已经看到..
Dialogue: 2,0:34:39.88,0:34:41.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You should know that we have already seen...
Dialogue: 3,0:34:41.48,0:34:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}... 你的一些账簿，并发现了一些问题
Dialogue: 2,0:34:41.48,0:34:44.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...some of your books and have several issues with it.
Dialogue: 3,0:34:45.08,0:34:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但恕我直言，先生..
Dialogue: 2,0:34:45.08,0:34:47.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But with due respect, sir...
Dialogue: 3,0:34:47.56,0:34:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}... 在财务问题上的误解是很自然的
Dialogue: 2,0:34:47.56,0:34:50.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...misunderstandings are natural in financial matters.
Dialogue: 3,0:34:50.96,0:34:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}由于没有充分了解，可能会产生误解
Dialogue: 2,0:34:50.96,0:34:53.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}There can be misinterpretation because of ignorance and...
Dialogue: 3,0:34:53.24,0:34:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你是说我们无知吗，特亚吉先生？
Dialogue: 2,0:34:53.24,0:34:55.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Are you calling us ignorant, Mr. Tyagi?
Dialogue: 3,0:34:56.56,0:34:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不是的，我相信你们都是很有学问的人
Dialogue: 2,0:34:56.56,0:34:59.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Not at all. I'm sure you all are very learned men.
Dialogue: 3,0:35:01.12,0:35:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但我们也是花旗银行
Dialogue: 2,0:35:01.12,0:35:02.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But we are also Citibank.
Dialogue: 3,0:35:03.44,0:35:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们在印度已经有90年了
Dialogue: 2,0:35:03.44,0:35:05.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We have been in India since 90 years.
Dialogue: 3,0:35:06.96,0:35:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们对这个国家非常忠诚
Dialogue: 2,0:35:06.96,0:35:08.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We are very committed to this country.
Dialogue: 3,0:35:10.28,0:35:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们已经投入了大笔资金
Dialogue: 2,0:35:10.28,0:35:12.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We have invested large sums of money.
Dialogue: 3,0:35:12.80,0:35:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}过去四年我们甚至没有分过红利
Dialogue: 2,0:35:12.80,0:35:14.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We haven't even taken any dividend for the last four years.
Dialogue: 3,0:35:16.68,0:35:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们在这个国家培育了 NRI 的投资
Dialogue: 2,0:35:16.68,0:35:19.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We have nurtured the NRI investment in this country.
Dialogue: 3,0:35:19.76,0:35:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们把数字设备公司带到了这个国家
Dialogue: 2,0:35:19.76,0:35:22.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We brought the Digital equipment corporation to this country.
Dialogue: 3,0:35:24.04,0:35:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不明白为什么成功在这里是一种犯罪
Dialogue: 2,0:35:24.04,0:35:28.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I don't understand why being successful is such a crime here.
Dialogue: 3,0:35:47.04,0:35:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你确定 CBI 在跟踪你吗
Dialogue: 2,0:35:47.04,0:35:48.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Venkitarajan] 'Are you sure the CBI is following you?'
Dialogue: 3,0:35:49.32,0:35:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“确定，我也在我家附近见过他们”
Dialogue: 2,0:35:49.32,0:35:51.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Sucheta] 'Yes, I've seen them near my house too.'
Dialogue: 3,0:35:51.48,0:35:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那我们就不能这样见面了
Dialogue: 2,0:35:51.48,0:35:52.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Then, we can't meet like this.
Dialogue: 3,0:35:54.64,0:35:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是还有一个人有兴趣见你
Dialogue: 2,0:35:54.64,0:35:57.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But there is someone else who is interested in meeting you.
Dialogue: 3,0:35:58.96,0:36:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不用说，这次会议是非正式的
Dialogue: 2,0:35:58.96,0:36:03.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Needless to say, this meeting will be unofficial.
Dialogue: 3,0:36:04.84,0:36:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你今天能去德里吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:36:04.84,0:36:06.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Can you go to Delhi today?
Dialogue: 3,0:36:07.28,0:36:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我想你应该去见一见
Dialogue: 2,0:36:07.28,0:36:10.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I think you should go. It could be an interesting meeting.
Dialogue: 3,0:36:15.84,0:36:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}CBI、政府和媒体..
Dialogue: 2,0:36:15.84,0:36:18.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}CBI, government and media...
Dialogue: 3,0:36:19.36,0:36:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}都把注意力集中在一个人身上
Dialogue: 2,0:36:19.36,0:36:21.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...are after one man.
Dialogue: 3,0:36:23.00,0:36:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但我认为我们应该转移注意力
Dialogue: 2,0:36:23.00,0:36:26.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But I think we should shift the focus.
Dialogue: 3,0:36:27.72,0:36:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}银行、国际银行..
Dialogue: 2,0:36:27.72,0:36:29.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Banks, International banks...
Dialogue: 3,0:36:30.16,0:36:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还有国有企业
Dialogue: 2,0:36:30.16,0:36:32.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...and government-owned companies.
Dialogue: 3,0:36:33.36,0:36:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}JPC的权力有限
Dialogue: 2,0:36:33.36,0:36:35.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}JPC has limited powers.
Dialogue: 3,0:36:36.04,0:36:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们也不是一个调查机构
Dialogue: 2,0:36:36.04,0:36:38.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And we are not an investigative body also.
Dialogue: 3,0:36:38.64,0:36:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们掌握了大量信息，但却无能为力
Dialogue: 2,0:36:38.64,0:36:42.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'We have tons of information but we can do nothing with it.'
Dialogue: 3,0:36:43.28,0:36:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}严格来说，我们不能公开
Dialogue: 2,0:36:43.28,0:36:45.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Technically, we can't make it public.
Dialogue: 3,0:36:46.08,0:36:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是你可以找到一种能让真相曝光的方式
Dialogue: 2,0:36:46.08,0:36:50.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But you can find a way to make it reach your readers.
Dialogue: 3,0:36:52.08,0:36:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一旦曝光..
Dialogue: 2,0:36:52.08,0:36:53.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Once it's out...
Dialogue: 3,0:36:54.72,0:36:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}中央调查局就会介入调查
Dialogue: 2,0:36:54.72,0:36:57.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...the CBI will have to investigate.
Dialogue: 3,0:36:57.76,0:36:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没有任何借口
Dialogue: 2,0:36:57.76,0:36:59.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They will have no excuse.
Dialogue: 3,0:37:00.52,0:37:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这些不仅仅是文件，而是系统的真相
Dialogue: 2,0:37:00.52,0:37:05.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}These are not just files, but the truth of the system. Truth.
Dialogue: 3,0:37:07.04,0:37:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是，你只能在这个房间里看
Dialogue: 2,0:37:07.04,0:37:10.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But yes, you can only do it in this room.
Dialogue: 3,0:37:10.68,0:37:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你不能把任何东西带出这个房间
Dialogue: 2,0:37:10.68,0:37:12.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You can't take anything out of this room.
Dialogue: 3,0:37:13.72,0:37:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}辛格先生还有更多的文件
Dialogue: 2,0:37:13.72,0:37:15.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Mr. Singh has more files.
Dialogue: 3,0:37:16.28,0:37:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他下午拿过来
Dialogue: 2,0:37:16.28,0:37:17.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He's getting it in the afternoon.
Dialogue: 3,0:37:54.68,0:37:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}给你，还需要什么就告诉我好吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:37:54.68,0:37:57.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Here you are. You need anything else, let me know, okay?
Dialogue: 3,0:38:06.40,0:38:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}有一些外资银行认为他们可以逃脱惩罚
Dialogue: 2,0:38:06.40,0:38:09.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}There are some foreign banks who thought they would get away with anything.
Dialogue: 3,0:38:09.64,0:38:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}玩弄银行收据，甚至没有保留记录以供核实
Dialogue: 2,0:38:09.64,0:38:14.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They made a mockery of bank receipts and did not even maintain proper records for verification.
Dialogue: 3,0:38:14.84,0:38:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们大量证券交易的一些文件都是... ..
Dialogue: 2,0:38:14.84,0:38:18.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Some of the documents of bulk of their securities deals are...
Dialogue: 3,0:38:19.08,0:38:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}消失了
Dialogue: 2,0:38:19.08,0:38:20.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...conveniently missing.
Dialogue: 3,0:38:21.24,0:38:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你可以查看所有的文件，然后问我任何你想问的问题
Dialogue: 2,0:38:21.24,0:38:24.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You can check all the papers and ask me anything you like.
Dialogue: 3,0:38:48.04,0:38:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ Sucheta ]“当我们深入研究JPC的报告和记录时... ... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:38:48.04,0:38:50.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Sucheta] 'As we dug deep into the JPC reports and records...'
Dialogue: 3,0:38:50.68,0:38:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“很明显，哈尔沙德 · 梅塔的骗局... ... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:38:50.68,0:38:53.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...it became very clear that the Harshad Mehta scam...'
Dialogue: 3,0:38:53.40,0:38:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}只是庞大银行系统违规行为的一小部分
Dialogue: 2,0:38:53.40,0:38:56.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...was a part of the bigger irregularities in the banking system.'
Dialogue: 3,0:38:57.04,0:38:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“哈沙德并没有创造违规手段... ... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:38:57.04,0:38:59.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Irregularities and flaws that Harshad didn't invent...'
Dialogue: 3,0:39:00.36,0:39:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“ ... 但他确实滥用了漏洞”
Dialogue: 2,0:39:00.36,0:39:02.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...but he misused them freely.'
Dialogue: 3,0:39:03.12,0:39:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“还有一点很清楚”
Dialogue: 2,0:39:03.12,0:39:04.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Another thing was clear.'
Dialogue: 3,0:39:04.80,0:39:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}与哈尔沙德•梅塔(Harshad Mehta)一样，调查银行也很重要... ..
Dialogue: 2,0:39:04.80,0:39:07.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Along with Harshad Mehta, it was important to investigate banks...'
Dialogue: 3,0:39:07.48,0:39:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}特别是花旗银行及其经纪人
Dialogue: 2,0:39:07.48,0:39:10.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...especially Citibank and its brokers.'
Dialogue: 3,0:39:11.24,0:39:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是彻底清理系统的唯一方法
Dialogue: 2,0:39:11.24,0:39:14.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'This was the only way to clean the system completely.'
Dialogue: 3,0:39:45.44,0:39:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，我同意我们的一些交易看起来有问题..
Dialogue: 2,0:39:45.44,0:39:48.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, I agree some of our dealings may look problematic...
Dialogue: 3,0:39:49.60,0:39:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们可能遭受了巨大的损失
Dialogue: 2,0:39:49.60,0:39:51.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...and we may have suffered some big losses.
Dialogue: 3,0:39:52.40,0:39:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但我向你保证，先生..
Dialogue: 2,0:39:52.40,0:39:53.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But let me assure you, sir...
Dialogue: 3,0:39:53.92,0:39:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们的 PMS 客户和老客户都没有损失
Dialogue: 2,0:39:53.92,0:39:58.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...that none of our PMS clients or our regular customers have lost any money.
Dialogue: 3,0:40:00.08,0:40:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}饶先生，这不仅仅关乎利润和损失
Dialogue: 2,0:40:00.08,0:40:03.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Mr. Rao, it's not only about profits and losses.
Dialogue: 3,0:40:04.04,0:40:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}人们一直在质疑你在货币市场上的运作方式
Dialogue: 2,0:40:04.04,0:40:07.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}People have been questioning the way you are operating in the money market.
Dialogue: 3,0:40:08.08,0:40:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}大家都在说，花旗银行是个恶霸
Dialogue: 2,0:40:08.08,0:40:11.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Everyone is saying, Citibank is a bully.
Dialogue: 3,0:40:11.76,0:40:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，那些说我们是恶霸的人..
Dialogue: 2,0:40:11.76,0:40:13.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, the people who are calling us a bully...
Dialogue: 3,0:40:14.20,0:40:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}都是那些无法与我们竞争的人
Dialogue: 2,0:40:14.20,0:40:16.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...are the same people who probably couldn't compete with us.
Dialogue: 3,0:40:17.72,0:40:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}让我帮您快速回忆一下，先生..
Dialogue: 2,0:40:17.72,0:40:19.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Let me refresh your memory quickly, sir...
Dialogue: 3,0:40:19.72,0:40:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们有多爱国
Dialogue: 2,0:40:19.72,0:40:21.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...of how patriotic we are...
Dialogue: 3,0:40:21.80,0:40:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}以及我们对这个国家有多忠诚
Dialogue: 2,0:40:21.80,0:40:25.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...and what our allegiance to this country means, to us.
Dialogue: 3,0:40:25.96,0:40:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}1990年，两年前..
Dialogue: 2,0:40:25.96,0:40:27.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}1990, just two years back...
Dialogue: 3,0:40:28.52,0:40:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}当印度被美国贸易代表卡拉・希尔斯控制的时候
Dialogue: 2,0:40:28.52,0:40:31.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...when India was under the hammer of US trade representative Carla Hills...
Dialogue: 3,0:40:32.28,0:40:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在国际收支危机期间
Dialogue: 2,0:40:32.28,0:40:33.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...during the balance of payments crisis.
Dialogue: 3,0:40:34.48,0:40:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是我坚决支持印度
Dialogue: 2,0:40:34.48,0:40:36.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It was I who stood strongly for India...
Dialogue: 3,0:40:36.96,0:40:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}反对美国威胁实施贸易制裁
Dialogue: 2,0:40:36.96,0:40:38.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...against the USA threat of trade sanctions.
Dialogue: 3,0:40:40.44,0:40:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果你还记得的话，先生，我们刊登了整版的亲印度广告
Dialogue: 2,0:40:40.44,0:40:43.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If you remember, sir, we ran full-page pro-India advertisements.
Dialogue: 3,0:40:44.20,0:40:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}只是为了证明我们有多爱国
Dialogue: 2,0:40:44.20,0:40:45.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Just to show how patriotic we are.
Dialogue: 3,0:40:47.20,0:40:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}然而，现在你却叫我们外国人
Dialogue: 2,0:40:47.20,0:40:51.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And look, today you are calling us foreigners.
Dialogue: 3,0:40:52.96,0:40:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}无论如何，我会尽我所能..
Dialogue: 2,0:40:52.96,0:40:56.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Anyway. I'm going to do my best and...
Dialogue: 3,0:40:56.68,0:40:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我会试着用我们的行动来满足你，先生
Dialogue: 2,0:40:56.68,0:40:58.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...I'll try and satisfy you with our actions, sir.
Dialogue: 3,0:40:59.56,0:41:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}希望如此
Dialogue: 2,0:40:59.56,0:41:00.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I hope so.
Dialogue: 3,0:41:02.00,0:41:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这些JPC的小丑一定是把消息泄露给了媒体
Dialogue: 2,0:41:02.00,0:41:05.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}These buffoons from the JPC must have leaked the information to the press.
Dialogue: 3,0:41:06.92,0:41:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这些小丑对印度的商业模式一无所知
Dialogue: 2,0:41:06.92,0:41:09.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}These jokers are clueless about how business is done in India.
Dialogue: 3,0:41:10.64,0:41:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我暂时搞定了财政部长
Dialogue: 2,0:41:10.64,0:41:12.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Now I may have handled the Finance Minister for the time being.
Dialogue: 3,0:41:14.12,0:41:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是因为我们所有的文件都经过了严格的审查..
Dialogue: 2,0:41:14.12,0:41:17.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But since all our documents are under intense scrutiny...
Dialogue: 3,0:41:17.76,0:41:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}媒体听证会随时都可能举行
Dialogue: 2,0:41:17.76,0:41:19.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...a press hearing can happen anytime.
Dialogue: 3,0:41:20.12,0:41:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是这些事情确实发生了
Dialogue: 2,0:41:20.12,0:41:21.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But these things happen.
Dialogue: 3,0:41:22.32,0:41:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没有必要担心
Dialogue: 2,0:41:22.32,0:41:24.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}There's no need to worry.
Dialogue: 3,0:41:25.80,0:41:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}再过几天，印度和巴基斯坦将举行板球比赛
Dialogue: 2,0:41:25.80,0:41:28.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}In a few days, there will be a cricket match between India and Pakistan...
Dialogue: 3,0:41:29.08,0:41:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}印度将击败巴基斯坦
Dialogue: 2,0:41:29.08,0:41:30.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...where India is going to defeat Pakistan...
Dialogue: 3,0:41:31.32,0:41:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}就这样，大家都会开心的
Dialogue: 2,0:41:31.32,0:41:33.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That's it. Everyone will be happy.
Dialogue: 3,0:41:34.04,0:41:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们会忘记一切
Dialogue: 2,0:41:34.04,0:41:35.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They will forget everything.
Dialogue: 3,0:41:37.40,0:41:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不这么认为
Dialogue: 2,0:41:37.40,0:41:38.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I don't think so.
Dialogue: 3,0:41:40.64,0:41:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}听着，是时候向前看了
Dialogue: 2,0:41:40.64,0:41:42.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look, it's time for you to move on.
Dialogue: 3,0:41:45.80,0:41:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你想说什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:41:45.80,0:41:47.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 3,0:41:48.60,0:41:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 你是要我辞职吗-不是
Dialogue: 2,0:41:48.60,0:41:50.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Are you asking me to resign? - No.
Dialogue: 3,0:41:51.44,0:41:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不是要你辞职
Dialogue: 2,0:41:51.44,0:41:53.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm not asking you to resign.
Dialogue: 3,0:41:53.64,0:41:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你是我们的明星
Dialogue: 2,0:41:53.64,0:41:55.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You've been our star performer.
Dialogue: 3,0:41:55.76,0:41:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你从财政部为我们赚了一大笔钱
Dialogue: 2,0:41:55.76,0:41:58.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You have earned us a fortune from the treasury department.
Dialogue: 3,0:41:58.76,0:42:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我是希望你能远离这次调查
Dialogue: 2,0:41:58.76,0:42:01.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'I just want you to stay away from this investigation.'
Dialogue: 3,0:42:02.72,0:42:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以恭喜你
Dialogue: 2,0:42:02.72,0:42:03.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So congratulations.
Dialogue: 3,0:42:04.76,0:42:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你被提拔到纽约总部了
Dialogue: 2,0:42:04.76,0:42:07.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You've been promoted and moved to New York.
Dialogue: 3,0:42:08.60,0:42:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}-不会吧？！-是的
Dialogue: 2,0:42:08.60,0:42:10.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- You're not serious. - I am.
Dialogue: 3,0:42:12.44,0:42:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在我要点菜单上最贵的酒
Dialogue: 2,0:42:12.44,0:42:15.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And now I'm going to order the most expensive wine on the menu.
Dialogue: 3,0:42:15.56,0:42:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你来买单
Dialogue: 2,0:42:15.56,0:42:17.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And unfortunately, you're going to be paying for it.
Dialogue: 3,0:42:18.36,0:42:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我希望你带了信用卡
Dialogue: 2,0:42:18.36,0:42:19.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I hope you're carrying your card.
Dialogue: 3,0:42:20.28,0:42:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这里是印度
Dialogue: 2,0:42:20.28,0:42:21.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This is India.
Dialogue: 3,0:42:23.12,0:42:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们只用现金
Dialogue: 2,0:42:23.12,0:42:24.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I only deal in cash.
Dialogue: 3,0:42:31.32,0:42:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你要在这种情况下去美国？
Dialogue: 2,0:42:31.32,0:42:33.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You're going to America in the middle of all this?
Dialogue: 3,0:42:34.00,0:42:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不是度假，管理层已经决定..
Dialogue: 2,0:42:34.00,0:42:37.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Not for a holiday. The management has decided this...
Dialogue: 3,0:42:38.16,0:42:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这对我们大家都好
Dialogue: 2,0:42:38.16,0:42:39.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...and it's the best for all of us.
Dialogue: 3,0:42:40.28,0:42:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}对大家都好？
Dialogue: 2,0:42:40.28,0:42:41.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}All of us? Ah!
Dialogue: 3,0:42:42.92,0:42:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还是对你和你的银行好？
Dialogue: 2,0:42:42.92,0:42:44.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Or for you and your bank?
Dialogue: 3,0:42:46.44,0:42:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们的办公室和住宅正遭到搜查
Dialogue: 2,0:42:46.44,0:42:48.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Our offices and homes are being raided.
Dialogue: 3,0:42:49.60,0:42:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}正在调查我们的账目
Dialogue: 2,0:42:49.60,0:42:51.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They are looking into our accounts.
Dialogue: 3,0:42:52.40,0:42:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}甚至逮捕了我，该死的，我还进了监狱
Dialogue: 2,0:42:52.40,0:42:55.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They even arrested me, goddamn it! I was in jail.
Dialogue: 3,0:42:55.92,0:42:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 但现在你出来了-是啊，保释了
Dialogue: 2,0:42:55.92,0:42:58.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- But now you're out. - Yeah, but on bail.
Dialogue: 3,0:42:58.76,0:43:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你知道他们提起了多少诉讼吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:42:58.76,0:43:01.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Do you have any idea how many cases they have filed against us?
Dialogue: 3,0:43:02.28,0:43:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不确定，但是没有他们起诉哈萨德的那么多
Dialogue: 2,0:43:02.28,0:43:05.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm not sure, but not as many as they have filed against Harshad.
Dialogue: 3,0:43:07.00,0:43:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在你觉得这很好笑了？
Dialogue: 2,0:43:07.00,0:43:08.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So now you think this is funny?
Dialogue: 3,0:43:09.52,0:43:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好了，AK! 放松
Dialogue: 2,0:43:09.52,0:43:11.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Come on, AK! Relax.
Dialogue: 3,0:43:12.52,0:43:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这个体系是有缺陷的
Dialogue: 2,0:43:12.52,0:43:13.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The system is flawed.
Dialogue: 3,0:43:14.68,0:43:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你不能对体系提起诉讼
Dialogue: 2,0:43:14.68,0:43:16.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And you can't file a case against a system.
Dialogue: 3,0:43:17.16,0:43:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不能逮捕系统
Dialogue: 2,0:43:17.16,0:43:18.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You can't arrest a system.
Dialogue: 3,0:43:18.56,0:43:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这一切很快就会平息下来
Dialogue: 2,0:43:18.56,0:43:20.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}All this is going to die down soon.
Dialogue: 3,0:43:21.44,0:43:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}保持低调
Dialogue: 2,0:43:21.44,0:43:22.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Just keep a low profile.
Dialogue: 3,0:43:23.96,0:43:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我得走了，杰瑞在等我
Dialogue: 2,0:43:23.96,0:43:26.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I must go now. Jerry is waiting for me.
Dialogue: 3,0:43:27.40,0:43:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是你们要保持联系，一切顺利
Dialogue: 2,0:43:27.40,0:43:30.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But you stay in touch. All the best.
Dialogue: 3,0:43:35.44,0:43:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在联合议会委员会之前，他甚至没有放过花旗银行..
Dialogue: 2,0:43:35.44,0:43:39.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Before the Joint Parliamentary Committee, he didn't even let Citibank go...
Dialogue: 3,0:43:39.84,0:43:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他会拿我们怎么办？
Dialogue: 2,0:43:39.84,0:43:41.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What will he do with us?
Dialogue: 3,0:43:42.96,0:43:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}等着瞧吧..
Dialogue: 2,0:43:42.96,0:43:44.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Wait and watch...
Dialogue: 3,0:43:44.72,0:43:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}等时机成熟，他会像电影英雄一样挺身而出
Dialogue: 2,0:43:44.72,0:43:48.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...when the time is right, he'll come forward like a film hero...
Dialogue: 3,0:43:48.08,0:43:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}把我们都供出来
Dialogue: 2,0:43:48.08,0:43:49.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...and rat us all out.
Dialogue: 3,0:43:50.80,0:43:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈尔沙德不是我们的敌人
Dialogue: 2,0:43:50.80,0:43:52.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad is not our enemy.
Dialogue: 3,0:43:54.16,0:43:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是他应该知道他有很多敌人
Dialogue: 2,0:43:54.16,0:43:56.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But he should know he has a lot of enemies.
Dialogue: 3,0:43:57.56,0:44:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}虽然我们不能把他送回监狱，但他应该永远害怕回去
Dialogue: 2,0:43:57.56,0:44:01.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Though we can't send him back to jail, he should always fear going back.
Dialogue: 3,0:44:02.44,0:44:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他应该每天做关于监狱的噩梦
Dialogue: 2,0:44:02.44,0:44:04.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He should have nightmares about jail.
Dialogue: 3,0:44:13.60,0:44:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}进来吧
Dialogue: 2,0:44:13.60,0:44:14.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Come in. Come on.
Dialogue: 3,0:44:16.12,0:44:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}开始，开始
Dialogue: 2,0:44:16.12,0:44:17.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Start, start.
Dialogue: 3,0:44:17.48,0:44:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 这是干什么? 阿什温!-搜查每个角落
Dialogue: 2,0:44:17.48,0:44:19.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- What is this? Ashwin! - Search every bloody corner.
Dialogue: 3,0:44:22.36,0:44:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}发生什么事了，长官？
Dialogue: 2,0:44:22.36,0:44:24.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What's going on, sir?
Dialogue: 3,0:44:26.32,0:44:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们有搜查令
Dialogue: 2,0:44:26.32,0:44:27.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We have a search warrant.
Dialogue: 3,0:44:28.60,0:44:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你家不是散步的海滨大道
Dialogue: 2,0:44:28.60,0:44:31.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Your house is not Marine Drive, that we have come here for a stroll.
Dialogue: 3,0:44:32.52,0:44:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 我们有可靠消息-什么消息？
Dialogue: 2,0:44:32.52,0:44:35.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- We have some solid information. - What information?
Dialogue: 3,0:44:35.80,0:44:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}发生了什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:44:35.80,0:44:36.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What happened?
Dialogue: 3,0:44:37.76,0:44:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你认识尼拉杰·沙阿吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:44:37.76,0:44:39.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Do you know Niraj Shah?
Dialogue: 3,0:44:41.64,0:44:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们见过几次面
Dialogue: 2,0:44:41.64,0:44:42.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We have met a couple of times.
Dialogue: 3,0:44:43.36,0:44:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}几次？
Dialogue: 2,0:44:43.36,0:44:44.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}A couple of times?
Dialogue: 3,0:44:45.28,0:44:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}根据我们的消息，你们两家关系很好
Dialogue: 2,0:44:45.28,0:44:49.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}According to our information, your families are very close.
Dialogue: 3,0:44:49.40,0:44:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还一起去度假
Dialogue: 2,0:44:49.40,0:44:52.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You go on holidays together.
Dialogue: 3,0:44:52.36,0:44:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们有共同的旅行策划人，是在一次假期中认识的
Dialogue: 2,0:44:52.36,0:44:55.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We have a common tour operator. We met during a holiday.
Dialogue: 3,0:44:56.24,0:44:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}高摩也会为他们理财，对吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:44:56.24,0:44:59.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Growmore handles their investments too, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:44:59.16,0:45:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}也许吧
Dialogue: 2,0:44:59.16,0:45:00.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Maybe.
Dialogue: 3,0:45:00.88,0:45:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你知道我们有多少客户吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:45:00.88,0:45:02.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Do you have any idea how many clients we have?
Dialogue: 3,0:45:02.68,0:45:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你知道尼拉杰做毒品生意吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:45:02.68,0:45:06.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Do you have any idea that Niraj has a narcotics business?
Dialogue: 3,0:45:08.60,0:45:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们怎么知道？
Dialogue: 2,0:45:08.60,0:45:09.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}How would we know?
Dialogue: 3,0:45:10.60,0:45:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他做什么生意，跟我们有什么关系？
Dialogue: 2,0:45:10.60,0:45:13.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And what business he does, how does it concern us?
Dialogue: 3,0:45:13.36,0:45:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不管与你有没有关系，我们来做决定，梅塔先生
Dialogue: 2,0:45:13.36,0:45:16.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Whether it concerns you or not, we will decide that, Mr. Mehta.
Dialogue: 3,0:45:18.32,0:45:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但如果你知道什么..
Dialogue: 2,0:45:18.32,0:45:19.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But if you know anything...
Dialogue: 3,0:45:20.52,0:45:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}自愿告诉我们
Dialogue: 2,0:45:20.52,0:45:21.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...tell us voluntarily.
Dialogue: 3,0:45:23.40,0:45:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}或者，你也知道我们可以再联系起来
Dialogue: 2,0:45:23.40,0:45:27.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Or, you know that we can make the connection.
Dialogue: 3,0:45:30.20,0:45:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}根本没有联系
Dialogue: 2,0:45:30.20,0:45:33.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It will have to be a made-up connection, because in reality there is none.
Dialogue: 3,0:45:33.52,0:45:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}梅塔先生，缉毒科..
Dialogue: 2,0:45:33.52,0:45:35.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Mr. Mehta, narcotics...
Dialogue: 3,0:45:36.68,0:45:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不像是股票市场的骗局
Dialogue: 2,0:45:36.68,0:45:38.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...is not like a share market scam.
Dialogue: 3,0:45:40.28,0:45:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你一定听说过 COFEPOSA
Dialogue: 2,0:45:40.28,0:45:42.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You must have heard about COFEPOSA.
Dialogue: 3,0:45:43.32,0:45:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}保护外汇和防止走私活动法
Dialogue: 2,0:45:43.32,0:45:46.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Conservation of Foreign Exchange and Prevention of Smuggling activities Act.
Dialogue: 3,0:45:48.28,0:45:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果你被起诉，你可以忘记过正常的生活
Dialogue: 2,0:45:48.28,0:45:51.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If you are charged with this, you can forget about living a normal life.
Dialogue: 3,0:45:52.76,0:45:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不是... 我不是在开玩笑好吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:45:52.76,0:45:56.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And I am not... I am not f*****g around, okay?
Dialogue: 3,0:45:57.52,0:45:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，我们什么也没找到
Dialogue: 2,0:45:57.52,0:45:58.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[CBI officer] 'Sir, we didn't find anything.'
Dialogue: 3,0:45:59.72,0:46:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哦！
Dialogue: 2,0:45:59.72,0:46:00.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Oh!
Dialogue: 3,0:46:03.04,0:46:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是可卡因... 不是你在厨房里可以找到的油炸小吃
Dialogue: 2,0:46:03.04,0:46:07.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's cocaine... not snacks that you'll find frying in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 3,0:46:10.28,0:46:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没有人在家经营毒品生意
Dialogue: 2,0:46:10.28,0:46:12.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No one conducts narcotics business from home.
Dialogue: 3,0:46:14.24,0:46:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我希望你没有忘记我们的办公室
Dialogue: 2,0:46:14.24,0:46:17.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I hope you haven't forgotten our office.
Dialogue: 3,0:46:19.00,0:46:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果你想起什么，请来找我们
Dialogue: 2,0:46:19.00,0:46:22.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If you remember anything, please pay us a visit.
Dialogue: 3,0:46:23.60,0:46:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果我们发现了什么，我会再把你关进去
Dialogue: 2,0:46:23.60,0:46:27.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And if we find something, we'll take you away.
Dialogue: 3,0:46:28.84,0:46:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:46:28.84,0:46:29.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Okay?
Dialogue: 3,0:46:32.24,0:46:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 大家快点，我们走-是，长官
Dialogue: 2,0:46:32.24,0:46:34.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Come on, everybody. Let's move. -[Officer] 'Yes, Sir.'
Dialogue: 3,0:46:39.72,0:46:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}缉毒科？
Dialogue: 2,0:46:39.72,0:46:40.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Narcotics?
Dialogue: 3,0:46:43.44,0:46:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 2,0:46:43.44,0:46:44.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What is going on?
Dialogue: 3,0:46:46.72,0:46:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果让他们安排，他们下一步就会称我们为恐怖分子
Dialogue: 2,0:46:46.72,0:46:48.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Left to them, they'll call us terrorists next.
Dialogue: 3,0:46:53.60,0:46:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们应该做好准备，接下来，他们会经常来突袭
Dialogue: 2,0:46:53.60,0:46:56.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We should get prepared. Now, they will regularly raid us.
Dialogue: 3,0:47:00.92,0:47:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们有摄像机，不是吗? 在哪里？
Dialogue: 2,0:47:00.92,0:47:03.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We had a video camera, didn't we? Where is it?
Dialogue: 3,0:47:05.96,0:47:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你用摄像机做什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:47:05.96,0:47:07.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What will you do with a video camera?
Dialogue: 3,0:47:09.44,0:47:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我要拍一部电影
Dialogue: 2,0:47:09.44,0:47:10.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'll make a film.
Dialogue: 3,0:47:12.12,0:47:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈尔沙德？
Dialogue: 2,0:47:12.12,0:47:13.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad?
Dialogue: 3,0:47:14.60,0:47:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我录这段视频是因为..
Dialogue: 2,0:47:14.60,0:47:16.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm recording this video because...
Dialogue: 3,0:47:17.12,0:47:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果我出了什么事，人们应该知道谁该为此负责
Dialogue: 2,0:47:17.12,0:47:21.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...if anything happens to me, people should know who is responsible.
Dialogue: 3,0:47:42.68,0:47:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}斯瓦米已经和我们断绝了一切关系，对吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:47:42.68,0:47:46.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Swami ji has severed all ties with us, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:47:50.40,0:47:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在是时候..
Dialogue: 2,0:47:50.40,0:47:51.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Now it's time...
Dialogue: 3,0:47:53.44,0:47:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}把那个大师从冥想中唤醒
Dialogue: 2,0:47:53.44,0:47:55.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...to wake that Swami from his meditation.
Dialogue: 3,0:47:59.00,0:48:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}政府和斯瓦米都应该知道..
Dialogue: 2,0:47:59.00,0:48:01.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The government and Swami should both know...
Dialogue: 3,0:48:02.92,0:48:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈沙德的不幸也会给他们蒙上阴影
Dialogue: 2,0:48:02.92,0:48:05.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...that Harshad's bad luck can also cast a shadow on them.
Dialogue: 3,0:48:10.52,0:48:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果他们想搞我……
Dialogue: 2,0:48:10.52,0:48:12.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If they try to f*** with me...
Dialogue: 3,0:48:14.64,0:48:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}整个国家会搞死他们
Dialogue: 2,0:48:14.64,0:48:16.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...the whole country will f*** them over.
Dialogue: 3,0:48:18.48,0:48:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我知道中央调查局是怎么运作的
Dialogue: 2,0:48:18.48,0:48:21.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I know how CBI works.
Dialogue: 3,0:48:23.00,0:48:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}它们被德里的皮带拴着
Dialogue: 2,0:48:23.00,0:48:27.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They are on Delhi's leash, and they bark on command.
Dialogue: 3,0:48:30.20,0:48:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}普拉纳夫，你真是个傻瓜
Dialogue: 2,0:48:30.20,0:48:33.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Pranav, you're a fool.
Dialogue: 3,0:48:35.56,0:48:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你一开始就应该带他来见我
Dialogue: 2,0:48:35.56,0:48:38.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You should have brought him to me right in the beginning.
Dialogue: 3,0:48:39.04,0:48:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那些自称出庭律师的蠢货.
Dialogue: 2,0:48:39.04,0:48:42.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Those foolish lawyers who call themselves barristers...
Dialogue: 3,0:48:42.52,0:48:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}连西装都不会穿
Dialogue: 2,0:48:42.52,0:48:45.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...and don't even know how to wear a coat properly...
Dialogue: 3,0:48:45.40,0:48:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你为什么要去找他们？
Dialogue: 2,0:48:45.40,0:48:46.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Why did you have to go to them?
Dialogue: 3,0:48:48.16,0:48:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}拉姆叔叔，你是司法之神
Dialogue: 2,0:48:48.16,0:48:51.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Ram uncle, you're the god of the judiciary.
Dialogue: 3,0:48:52.00,0:48:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们觉得这件事太小了，不值得上帝去操心
Dialogue: 2,0:48:52.00,0:48:55.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We felt this was too small a matter, to trouble God with.
Dialogue: 3,0:48:55.80,0:48:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们不知道这场战争会持续到
Dialogue: 2,0:48:55.80,0:48:58.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We didn't know this war would drag on for so long...
Dialogue: 3,0:48:58.64,0:49:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}PMO进入战场
Dialogue: 2,0:48:58.64,0:49:00.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...that the PMO would enter the battlefield.
Dialogue: 3,0:49:01.52,0:49:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}于是我以上帝的名义把哈沙德带到这里
Dialogue: 2,0:49:01.52,0:49:04.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So I took God's name and brought Harshad here.
Dialogue: 3,0:49:05.20,0:49:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}别再用上帝这个词来讨好我了
Dialogue: 2,0:49:05.20,0:49:07.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Stop buttering me up with this 'God' business.
Dialogue: 3,0:49:09.12,0:49:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这段时间，你一直生活在上帝的怜悯之中
Dialogue: 2,0:49:09.12,0:49:11.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}All this while, you were living on god's mercy.
Dialogue: 3,0:49:13.00,0:49:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是现在你得依法办事了
Dialogue: 2,0:49:13.00,0:49:15.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But now you'll have to work with the law.
Dialogue: 3,0:49:17.32,0:49:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈沙德..
Dialogue: 2,0:49:17.32,0:49:18.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad...
Dialogue: 3,0:49:19.16,0:49:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你给首相的一千万
Dialogue: 2,0:49:19.16,0:49:21.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...the one crore that you gave the PM...
Dialogue: 3,0:49:22.48,0:49:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}有跟别人提过吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:49:22.48,0:49:24.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...did you tell anyone about it?
Dialogue: 3,0:49:25.72,0:49:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还没有
Dialogue: 2,0:49:25.72,0:49:26.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Not yet.
Dialogue: 3,0:49:27.76,0:49:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 但我可以证明-我的工作就是证明
Dialogue: 2,0:49:27.76,0:49:31.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- But I can prove it. - It's my job to prove.
Dialogue: 3,0:49:32.52,0:49:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我是你的律师
Dialogue: 2,0:49:32.52,0:49:33.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm your lawyer.
Dialogue: 3,0:49:35.16,0:49:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}听着，现在..
Dialogue: 2,0:49:35.16,0:49:37.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And listen, now...
Dialogue: 3,0:49:37.68,0:49:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}警察局和中央调查局，不管他们问什么
Dialogue: 2,0:49:37.68,0:49:40.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...the police, CBI... whatever they ask...
Dialogue: 3,0:49:41.36,0:49:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“没有我的允许，你不能开口”
Dialogue: 2,0:49:41.36,0:49:45.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'You will not talk to them without consulting me.'
Dialogue: 3,0:49:45.80,0:49:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“你明白吗? ”
Dialogue: 2,0:49:45.80,0:49:46.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Do you understand?'
Dialogue: 3,0:49:52.92,0:49:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}1991年11月2日到4日，你提取了一些大额款项
Dialogue: 2,0:49:52.92,0:49:57.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}In 1991, between 2nd and 4th November, you made some large withdrawals.
Dialogue: 3,0:49:59.48,0:50:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}从格林德莱斯银行提现100万卢比
Dialogue: 2,0:49:59.48,0:50:02.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Ten lakh rupees from Grindlays Bank, Fort branch.
Dialogue: 3,0:50:04.00,0:50:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}从印度国家银行提现300万卢比
Dialogue: 2,0:50:04.00,0:50:06.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Thirty lakhs from SBI's main branch.
Dialogue: 3,0:50:06.92,0:50:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还有11月4日在德里的两次提现
Dialogue: 2,0:50:06.92,0:50:08.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And two withdrawals in Delhi on 4th November.
Dialogue: 3,0:50:09.20,0:50:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}450万卢比
Dialogue: 2,0:50:09.20,0:50:10.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Forty-five lakhs.
Dialogue: 3,0:50:12.36,0:50:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你怎么会有这么多现金？
Dialogue: 2,0:50:12.36,0:50:15.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What were you doing with so much cash?
Dialogue: 3,0:50:17.40,0:50:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我什么都不记得了，这些都是很久以前的交易
Dialogue: 2,0:50:17.40,0:50:19.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I don't remember anything. These are very old transactions.
Dialogue: 3,0:50:20.08,0:50:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是一大笔钱，梅塔先生
Dialogue: 2,0:50:20.08,0:50:21.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's a big amount, Mr. Mehta.
Dialogue: 3,0:50:22.52,0:50:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}试着回忆一下
Dialogue: 2,0:50:22.52,0:50:23.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Try to remember.
Dialogue: 3,0:50:24.80,0:50:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}听着，这对你来说可能是一大笔钱，但对我来说不是
Dialogue: 2,0:50:24.80,0:50:27.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look, this might be a big amount for you, not for me.
Dialogue: 3,0:50:28.24,0:50:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我真的不记得了
Dialogue: 2,0:50:28.24,0:50:29.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I really don't remember.
Dialogue: 3,0:50:33.52,0:50:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果你想起来的话记得告诉我
Dialogue: 2,0:50:33.52,0:50:35.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Let me know if you remember.
Dialogue: 3,0:50:38.60,0:50:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你不应该在那里说一个字
Dialogue: 2,0:50:38.60,0:50:41.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You shouldn't have uttered a single word there.
Dialogue: 3,0:50:42.24,0:50:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你为什么让他说话？
Dialogue: 2,0:50:42.24,0:50:43.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Why did you let him speak?
Dialogue: 3,0:50:44.04,0:50:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 你不明白吗?-但我说什么了？
Dialogue: 2,0:50:44.04,0:50:46.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Don't you understand? - But what did I say?
Dialogue: 3,0:50:47.04,0:50:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你不是说你不记得钱的事了吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:50:47.04,0:50:49.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Didn't you say that you don't remember anything about the money?
Dialogue: 3,0:50:50.40,0:50:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以‘我不记得了’并不意味着我说了什么
Dialogue: 2,0:50:50.40,0:50:51.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So 'I don't remember' doesn't mean I said anything.
Dialogue: 3,0:50:52.24,0:50:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你不知道他们是怎么把这个‘我不记得’变成证据的
Dialogue: 2,0:50:52.24,0:50:55.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You have no idea how they can turn this 'I don't remember' into evidence.
Dialogue: 3,0:50:56.48,0:51:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}幸好中央调查局的审讯记录在法庭上不能作为证据
Dialogue: 2,0:50:56.48,0:51:00.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Thank God CBI's interrogation is not admissible in court.
Dialogue: 3,0:51:01.36,0:51:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}否则你就废了
Dialogue: 2,0:51:01.36,0:51:03.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Or you would have let the PM off the hook.
Dialogue: 3,0:51:06.20,0:51:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}无论如何
Dialogue: 2,0:51:06.20,0:51:06.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Anyway.
Dialogue: 3,0:51:08.36,0:51:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我会处理好这个达斯局长
Dialogue: 2,0:51:08.36,0:51:10.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I will take care of this Das.
Dialogue: 3,0:51:13.36,0:51:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}怎么做？
Dialogue: 2,0:51:13.36,0:51:14.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}How?
Dialogue: 3,0:51:14.12,0:51:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}致中央调查局局长达斯先生
Dialogue: 2,0:51:14.12,0:51:17.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}To Mr. KS Das, CBI Chief.
Dialogue: 3,0:51:18.44,0:51:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}中央调查局询过问我的委托人
Dialogue: 2,0:51:18.44,0:51:21.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The cash withdrawals made by my client...
Dialogue: 3,0:51:21.76,0:51:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈沙德・尚蒂拉尔・梅塔先生
Dialogue: 2,0:51:21.76,0:51:24.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...Mr. Harshad Shantilal Mehta...
Dialogue: 3,0:51:24.76,0:51:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在1991年11月2日和4日之间
Dialogue: 2,0:51:24.76,0:51:27.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...between 2nd and 4th November, 1991...
Dialogue: 3,0:51:28.12,0:51:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}提取的现金
Dialogue: 2,0:51:28.12,0:51:30.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...about which CBI questioned him...
Dialogue: 3,0:51:31.12,0:51:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这个问题是政治敏感的
Dialogue: 2,0:51:31.12,0:51:33.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...are politically sensitive in nature...
Dialogue: 3,0:51:34.40,0:51:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“ ... 梅塔先生可以透露有关现金的用途... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:51:34.40,0:51:39.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...and Mr. Mehta can disclose details regarding them...'
Dialogue: 3,0:51:39.52,0:51:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}... 除非他能免受政治迫害
Dialogue: 2,0:51:39.52,0:51:44.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...only if he gets immunity from political persecution.'
Dialogue: 3,0:51:52.64,0:51:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Kiran?-怎么了？
Dialogue: 2,0:51:52.64,0:51:53.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Kiran? - Yeah?
Dialogue: 3,0:51:53.72,0:51:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你读过《商业标准》的新报道了吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:51:53.72,0:51:55.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Did you read Business Standard's new story?
Dialogue: 3,0:51:56.48,0:51:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 什么报道?-他们发表了一封信..
Dialogue: 2,0:51:56.48,0:51:58.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- What story? - They have published a letter...
Dialogue: 3,0:51:58.16,0:52:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}杰斯马拉尼写信给中央调查局局长
Dialogue: 2,0:51:58.16,0:52:00.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...that Jethmalani wrote to the CBI chief.
Dialogue: 3,0:52:00.24,0:52:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他在信中宣称哈沙德可能贿赂了在政府里很有权势的人
Dialogue: 2,0:52:00.24,0:52:02.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}In it, he alleges that Harshad might have paid off someone...
Dialogue: 3,0:52:02.32,0:52:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}大概一千万左右
Dialogue: 2,0:52:02.32,0:52:04.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...very powerful in the government. Around one crore or something.
Dialogue: 3,0:52:04.84,0:52:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}称之为政治敏感
Dialogue: 2,0:52:04.84,0:52:06.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Calls it politically sensitive.
Dialogue: 3,0:52:06.52,0:52:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你知道可能是谁吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:52:06.52,0:52:08.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Do you have any idea who it might be?
Dialogue: 3,0:52:11.72,0:52:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以现在你也开始在媒体上制造谣言
Dialogue: 2,0:52:11.72,0:52:13.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'So now you're creating rumours in the press also?'
Dialogue: 3,0:52:18.16,0:52:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不做这么冒险的空头头寸，我是大公牛
Dialogue: 2,0:52:18.16,0:52:22.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I don't take such risky short positions. I am the big bull.
Dialogue: 3,0:52:24.28,0:52:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在，我只是制造了一个谣言
Dialogue: 2,0:52:24.28,0:52:25.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}For now, I've just created a rumour.
Dialogue: 3,0:52:27.60,0:52:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是搞不好... 首相可能会失去他的价值和他的政府..
Dialogue: 2,0:52:27.60,0:52:31.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But you never know... the Prime Minister might lose both his value and his government...
Dialogue: 3,0:52:31.96,0:52:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你真的认为，如果这些无稽之谈公之于众，会有所不同吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:52:31.96,0:52:35.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Do you really think, if this nonsense goes public, it will make a difference?
Dialogue: 3,0:52:41.20,0:52:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你觉得..
Dialogue: 2,0:52:41.20,0:52:42.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Do you think...
Dialogue: 3,0:52:44.12,0:52:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你是来喝橙汁的吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:52:44.12,0:52:45.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...you've been sent here to drink orange juice?
Dialogue: 3,0:52:48.00,0:52:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你是来谈判的对吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:52:48.00,0:52:49.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You're here to negotiate, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:52:51.08,0:52:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所有指控我们的案件都必须撤销
Dialogue: 2,0:52:51.08,0:52:53.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}All the cases against us should be withdrawn.
Dialogue: 3,0:52:55.08,0:52:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}梅塔先生，我们没有魔杖..
Dialogue: 2,0:52:55.08,0:52:59.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Mr. Harshad Mehta, we don't have a magic wand...
Dialogue: 3,0:52:59.88,0:53:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}可以让一切在一夜之间消失
Dialogue: 2,0:52:59.88,0:53:01.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...which can make everything disappear overnight.
Dialogue: 3,0:53:02.48,0:53:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所得税，中央调查局，媒体，每个人都在追查你..
Dialogue: 2,0:53:02.48,0:53:05.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Income tax, CBI, press, everyone is after you...
Dialogue: 3,0:53:05.68,0:53:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我知道... 所有人都在追查我
Dialogue: 2,0:53:05.68,0:53:07.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I know... Everyone is after me.
Dialogue: 3,0:53:08.80,0:53:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}有时候我觉得，他们甚至会起诉我在证交所扔炸弹
Dialogue: 2,0:53:08.80,0:53:12.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sometimes I feel, they'll even accuse me of the bomb blast at BSE.
Dialogue: 3,0:53:15.28,0:53:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}CBI 已经用 COFEPOSA 威胁我了
Dialogue: 2,0:53:15.28,0:53:17.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}CBI is already threatening me with COFEPOSA.
Dialogue: 3,0:53:17.92,0:53:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们还会以 TADA 罪起诉我
Dialogue: 2,0:53:17.92,0:53:19.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They'll charge me with TADA too.
Dialogue: 3,0:53:21.08,0:53:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一定会有些斡旋余地的
Dialogue: 2,0:53:21.08,0:53:23.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}There has to be some middle ground.
Dialogue: 3,0:53:25.60,0:53:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你一定要把嘴闭严
Dialogue: 2,0:53:25.60,0:53:27.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You just keep your mouth zipped.
Dialogue: 3,0:53:28.12,0:53:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我看看能帮上什么忙
Dialogue: 2,0:53:28.12,0:53:31.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'll see how you can be helped.
Dialogue: 3,0:53:32.32,0:53:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我要书面的
Dialogue: 2,0:53:32.32,0:53:33.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I want it in writing.
Dialogue: 3,0:53:34.60,0:53:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}以书面形式？
Dialogue: 2,0:53:34.60,0:53:35.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}In writing?
Dialogue: 3,0:53:37.08,0:53:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 这是 Jethmalani 先生的主意吗?-他是我们的律师
Dialogue: 2,0:53:37.08,0:53:39.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Is this Mr. Jethmalani's idea? - He's our lawyer.
Dialogue: 3,0:53:41.40,0:53:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}当然，他会考虑我们的安全
Dialogue: 2,0:53:41.40,0:53:43.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Naturally, he will think about our safety.
Dialogue: 3,0:53:44.00,0:53:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我要书面的
Dialogue: 2,0:53:44.00,0:53:45.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I want it in writing.
Dialogue: 3,0:53:47.64,0:53:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不可能用书面形式给出任何东西
Dialogue: 2,0:53:47.64,0:53:48.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's impossible to give anything in writing.
Dialogue: 3,0:53:49.60,0:53:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“我们只能做到这种程度”
Dialogue: 2,0:53:49.60,0:53:50.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'This is all that we can offer.'
Dialogue: 3,0:53:51.52,0:53:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在你来决定，你想怎么样？
Dialogue: 2,0:53:51.52,0:53:54.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Now you decide. What would you like to do?
Dialogue: 3,0:54:06.72,0:54:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}有这样的人群和这样的热情..
Dialogue: 2,0:54:06.72,0:54:09.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}With this kind of a crowd and this kind of a heat...
Dialogue: 3,0:54:09.68,0:54:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}让我结束所有的猜测，盖棺论定
Dialogue: 2,0:54:09.68,0:54:14.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...let me put an end to all the speculations and make it official.
Dialogue: 3,0:54:14.44,0:54:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这个骗局是
Dialogue: 2,0:54:14.44,0:54:17.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The scam was encouraged...
Dialogue: 3,0:54:18.52,0:54:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}由政府发起和支持的
Dialogue: 2,0:54:18.52,0:54:21.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...initiated and sustained by the government.
Dialogue: 3,0:54:21.36,0:54:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一千万现金支付给了尊敬的纳拉辛哈·拉奥
Dialogue: 2,0:54:21.36,0:54:25.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The money of rupees one crore was paid to honourable PV Narasimha Rao...
Dialogue: 3,0:54:26.24,0:54:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}印度总理
Dialogue: 2,0:54:26.24,0:54:27.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...the Prime Minister of India.
Dialogue: 3,0:54:28.08,0:54:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}手提箱和钱都按照总理的指示
Dialogue: 2,0:54:28.08,0:54:33.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And the suitcase and the money was left with Mr. Khandekar...
Dialogue: 3,0:54:33.88,0:54:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}留给了坎德卡先生..
Dialogue: 2,0:54:33.88,0:54:36.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...the personal assistant to the Prime Minister...
Dialogue: 3,0:54:37.16,0:54:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}首相的私人助理
Dialogue: 2,0:54:37.16,0:54:39.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...at the Prime Minister's suggestion.
Dialogue: 3,0:54:40.16,0:54:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}人们不会给骗局以人命名
Dialogue: 2,0:54:40.16,0:54:43.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}People don't give any human name to scams.
Dialogue: 3,0:54:43.40,0:54:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但如果这个骗局要用人的名字..
Dialogue: 2,0:54:43.40,0:54:46.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But if a human name is to be given to this scam...
Dialogue: 3,0:54:46.56,0:54:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这不是哈尔沙德·梅塔的骗局
Dialogue: 2,0:54:46.56,0:54:49.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...it is not the Harshad Mehta scam.
Dialogue: 3,0:54:50.08,0:54:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是总理的骗局
Dialogue: 2,0:54:50.08,0:54:51.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It is a PV Narasimha Rao scam.